'''珍妮·达米塔·乔·杰克逊'''<ref>“珍妮”或译“珍妮特”。</ref>（{{lang-en|Janet Damita Jo Jackson}}，{{bd|1966年|5月16日}}），是擁有十首[[公告牌百强单曲榜|公告牌百强单曲榜]]冠軍單曲及五座[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]的[[美国|美国]]著名唱片[[歌手|歌手]]与[[女演员|女演员]]。以发行一系列前卫音乐风格、社会广泛争议题材以及强烈[[性暗示|性暗示]]的唱片，以及出色的现场舞台表演效果而闻名于世。 除了歌唱事业之外她也跨足电视以及电影表演领域，这也使得她在25年以来一直都是流行文化中的指标性人物。根据《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志的统计，她是演艺圈中最富有的女性之一，个人资产达到1.5亿[[美元|美元]]。她是演艺圈传奇家族[[傑克森家族|杰克逊家族]]中最小的孩子（排行第九），并与她的兄长[[迈克尔·杰克逊|-{zh-hans:迈克尔·杰克逊;zh-hk:米高·積遜;zh-tw:麥可·傑克遜;}-]]一起成为20世纪80年代至今以来，流行音乐界的重要符号之一。1976年，她在描写自己家族的电视真人影辑《{{tsl|en|The Jacksons (TV series)|杰克逊一家}}》（The Jacksons）中出道，随后又在70年代末至80年代初出演了多部电视剧，包括：《[[美好时光|美好时光]]》（Good Times）以及《[[名扬四海|名扬四海]]》（Fame）。

在1982年，她与[[A&M唱片公司|A&M唱片公司]]签约，开始了自己的歌唱事业。而她的第三张录音室专辑《[[控制_(珍娜傑克森專輯)|控制]]》(1986)则令她开始成为流行偶像。她与著名音乐制作人{{tsl|en|Jimmy Jam and Terry Lewis|Jimmy Jam和Terry Lewis}}合作，开创性的将[[节奏布鲁斯|节奏布鲁斯]]、[[放克|放克]]、[[迪斯科|迪斯科]]、[[饶舌|饶舌]]以及[[工业噪音音乐|工业噪音音乐]]融合到[[流行音乐|流行音乐]]之中，成为当时音乐界的时尚先驱。随后，他们又将这种创新通过唱片、舞美效果、音乐录影带、广播以及新兴的[[音乐电视网|MTV电视台]]发扬光大，而珍妮亲自撰写的富含现实意义的歌词，也是她音乐作品的特色之一。

进入90年代，珍妮已成为了各大唱片公司追逐签约炙手可热的巨星。1991年，她与[[维京唱片|维京唱片]]签下了一张具体金额保密但保守估计高达数千万美元的唱片合约。这使她成为当时音乐史上最高签约费的歌手。在[[维京唱片|维京唱片]]旗下发行的首张专辑《[[Janet_(專輯)|珍娜]]》(1993)取得了爆炸性的成功，完美的塑造了她[[性感符号|性感符号]]的形象并延续至今。同年，珍妮主演了自己的第一部电影《{{tsl|en|Poetic Justice (film)|写诗的贾斯廷斯}}》(Poetic Justice)。90年代末，《[[公告牌|公告牌]]》杂志评选她为十年来最成功的女歌手第二位（仅次于[[玛丽亚·凯莉|玛丽亚·凯莉]]）。而她创作的一系列金曲《[[:en:Nasty_(song)|Nasty]]》、《[[節奏國度|節奏國度]]》、《[[愛就是這樣_(珍納·積遜歌曲)|愛就是這樣]]》、 《[[Together_Again_(珍娜·傑克森單曲)|再度重逢]]》和《[[All_for_You_(珍娜·傑克森單曲)|都給你]]》都成为乐坛经典之一。

珍妮·杰克逊凭借全世界累积唱片销量过亿的成绩，使她成为[[流行音乐|流行音乐]]史上'''[[:en:List_of_best-selling_music_artists|销量最高的艺人]]'''之一。<ref name="PR">{{citation|title=珍妮·杰克逊发行自己的新歌+精选专辑《Number Ones》|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/janet-jacksons-greatest-hits-celebrated-on-number-ones-64079852.html|publisher=[[:en:PR_Newswire|PR Newswire]]|place={{tsl|en|Universal Music Enterprises|Universal Music Enterprises}}|date=2009-10-14|accessdate=2009-10-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68iUOiAB7?url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/janet-jacksons-greatest-hits-celebrated-on-number-ones-64079852.html|archive-date=2012-06-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[美国唱片业协会|美国唱片业协会]]（RIAA）也以26白金的认证评的成绩，评定她为'''[[:en:List_of_best-selling_music_artists_in_the_United_States|美国销量最高的艺人榜]]'''女歌手的十一位。<ref>{{Citation | title = Top Selling Artists | publisher = [[美国唱片业协会|美国唱片业协会]] | url = http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?table=tblTopArt | accessdate = 2008-09-03 | archive-date = 2012-05-21 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/67pubQ275?url=http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?table=tblTopArt | dead-url = no }}</ref>2008年，《[[公告牌|公告牌]]》杂志发布了
'''[[公告牌百强单曲榜|公告牌百强单曲榜]][[:en:Billboard_Hot_100_50th_Anniversary_Charts#All-Time_top_artists|50年成绩总结]]'''，珍妮位列第七位。在2010年该杂志'''25年来50位最佳节奏布鲁斯/嘻哈音乐人'''的评选中，珍妮位列第五位。

作为世界上获奖最多的音乐人之一，她长青的表演状态、先锋的音乐理念、杰出的销量成绩和巨大的社会影响力，重新塑造和定义了20世纪80年代至今以来的流行音乐，也成为了许多音乐家的创作灵感。

曾與R&B男歌手[[约翰尼·吉尔|约翰尼·吉尔]]交往。2017年珍娜與最後一任前夫育有她唯一一位孩子。2019年，珍妮·杰克逊入選[[搖滾名人堂|搖滾名人堂]]。<ref>{{cite web| year = 2019| url = https://www.rockhall.com/2019-inductees/janet-jackson| title = Janet Jackson| publisher = Rock and Roll Hall of Fame| accessdate = December 13, 2019| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181213214009/https://www.rockhall.com/2019-inductees/janet-jackson/| archive-date = 2018-12-13| dead-url = yes}}</ref>

== 生活及事业 ==
=== 1966-1982：童年与电视工作 ===
[[Image:Jacksonstvshow.jpg|180px]]
珍妮·杰克逊出生于[[美国|美国]][[印第安纳州|印第安纳州]][[加里_(印第安纳州)|加里]]市聖瑪麗憐憫醫院，是[[凯瑟琳·杰克森|凯瑟琳·杰克森]]与[[约瑟夫·杰克森|约瑟夫·杰克森]]的第十个孩子（其中一子布兰登·杰克森早夭）<ref name="JJ by Cornwell">{{Citation | last = Cornwell | first = Jane| title = Janet Jackson | publisher={{tsl|en|Carlton Books|Carlton Books}} | year = 2002 | pages = 2, 10, 24 | isbn = 1-84222-464-6}}</ref>
杰克逊一家位于社会的中下层阶级，并且是虔诚的[[耶和华见证人|耶和华见证人]]派的教徒。虽然珍妮从小被作为一个耶和华见证人派而抚养长大，但是成年之后就没有再遵循教派的教义和意见生活。珍妮自己也形容自己与上帝的关系是独特的“一对一”般的。<ref>{{citation|last=Norment|first=Lynn|title=Janet: On her sexuality, spirituality, failed marriages, and lessons learned|newspaper=[[Jet_(magazine)|Jet]]|volume=57|issue=1|page=104|date=November 2001|issn=0012-9011}}</ref>作为杰克逊家族的老幺，当她还在蹒跚学步的时候，她的兄长[[傑奇·傑克森|杰基]]、[[狄托·傑克森|蒂托]]、[[傑曼·傑克森|杰梅因]]、[[馬龍·傑克森|马龙]]和[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔]]就组成了[[杰克逊五人组|杰克逊五人组]]在夜总会和剧院演出。1969年3月，[[杰克逊五人组|杰克逊五人组]]与[[摩城唱片|摩城唱片]]签下一纸合约。随着组合在[[摩城唱片|摩城唱片]]旗下推出4支单曲相继成为冠军而取得的成功，杰克逊一家的生活得以改善，并得以搬到[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]的{{tsl|en|Encino, Los Angeles|圣栎郡}}。<ref name="JJ by Cornwell"/>虽然出生于一个音乐世家，但是珍妮从小更希望长大之后成为一名赛马骑师而不是一个艺人。儘管如此，她的父亲仍然安排她向娱乐事业发展。珍妮曾经说：”从来没有人问过我是不是想进入娱乐圈...这都已经是安排好的。(No one ever asked me if I wanted to go into show business ... it was expected.)“<ref name="JJ by Cornwell"/>

1973年珍妮7岁时，她在她兄姊在[[拉斯维加斯|拉斯维加斯]]美高梅赌场的歌舞秀中登场。在Jane Cornwell2002年发行的为珍妮所撰写的传记《Janet Jackson》中提到，在珍妮8岁那年，她的父亲约瑟夫告诉她不能再叫他「爸爸」了，因为他是她的经纪人。从此之后，她将直接称呼他为「约瑟夫」。<ref name="JJ by Cornwell"/>她作为一名演员在[[CBS|CBS]]1976年的拍摄的描写她家庭的真人影辑《{{tsl|en|The Jacksons (TV series)|杰克逊一家}}》(The Jacksons)正式出道。在剧中与她的兄姊、[[瑞比·傑克森|瑞比]]、[[史蒂文·蘭道爾·蘭迪·傑克遜|兰迪]]、[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔]]、[[狄托·傑克森|蒂托]]、[[馬龍·傑克森|马龙]]、[[拉托亞·傑克森|拉托亞]]和[[傑奇·傑克森|杰基]]共同演出。<ref name="JJ by Cornwell"/>1977年，她被制作人{{tsl|en|Norman Lear|Norman Lear}}选中，在情景喜剧《[[美好时光|美好时光]]》(Good Times)中饰演Penny Gordon Woods。<ref name="JJ by Cornwell"/>1979年至1980年，她又在电视剧《{{tsl|en|A New Kind of Family|新式家庭}}》(A New Kind of Family)中饰演Jojo Ashton，1981年至1982年的电视剧《{{tsl|en|Diff'rent Strokes|细路仔}}》(Diff'rent Strokes)中也看得到她的身影。<ref name="JJ by Cornwell"/>1982年起，她在电视剧《[[名扬四海|名扬四海]]》(Fame)中饰演了主要角色Cleo Hewitt，并参演了四个播映季。事后珍妮承认，这份工作并不是她所喜欢的。<ref>{{Citation | last = Fox | first = Norman | title = ''Indian Summer'' | publisher = tv.com | url = http://www.tv.com/fame/indian-summer/episode/77620/summary.html | accessdate = 2008-09-03 | archive-date = 2012-11-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121108042131/http://www.tv.com/fame/indian-summer/episode/77620/summary.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Saunders">{{Citation |last= Saunders |first= Michael | title=The 3 Divas Janet Jackson turns her focus inward | newspaper=[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]] | page=D13 | date=1996-10-03}}</ref>

=== 1982–1985：早期唱片 ===
虽然珍妮对发展自己的音乐事业并不是特别的热衷，但是她还是同意和她的家庭成员一起录制唱片。1978年，她和她的哥哥[[史蒂文·蘭道爾·蘭迪·傑克遜|兰迪]]一起出版发行了一张名为《Love Song for Kids》的唱片。当16岁的时候，她的父亲安排她与[[A&M唱片公司|A&M唱片公司]]签约。<ref name="JJ by Cornwell"/>她的首张个人专辑《[[:en:Janet_Jackson_(album)|Janet Jackson]]》也於同年发行，专辑由[[灵魂音乐|灵魂音乐]]歌手{{tsl|en|Angela Winbush|Angela Winbush}}、{{tsl|en|René Moore|René Moore}}和Leon F. Sylvers III制作，并由她的父亲全程监制。<ref name="JJ by Cornwell"/>专辑在[[公告牌|公告牌]]R&B专辑榜上最高排名第六。<ref name="Billboard Album peaks">{{Citation | title = Janet Jackson |publisher=Allmusic | year = 2006 | url = {{Allmusic|class=artist|id=p4572|pure_url=yes}}| accessdate = 2008-04-13}}</ref>

珍妮的第二张专辑《{{tsl|en|Dream Street (Janet Jackson album)|Dream Street}}》与两年后发行。她的父亲找来了她的兄弟帮助完成这张专辑。[[馬龍·傑克森|马龙]]负责编写了两首歌曲，而[[狄托·傑克森|蒂托]]、[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔]]和[[傑奇·傑克森|杰基]]负责和声。<ref name="JJ by Cornwell"/>该专辑在R&B榜上最高排名第19位，销量也较上一张专辑差。<ref name="Billboard Album peaks"/>专辑中唯一一首热门歌曲《{{tsl|en|Don't Stand Another Chance|Don't Stand Another Chance}}》也只在公告牌R&B单曲榜上排名第九。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/#/charts/r-b-hip-hop-songs?chartDate=1984-10-20 |title=Top Hip-Hop and R&B Songs & Singles Charts |work=Billboard |accessdate=2010-06-12 |archive-date=2012-07-28 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120728/http://www.billboard.com/%23/artist/eddie-murphy/chart-history/1173?f=305&g=Albums#/charts/r-b-hip-hop-songs?chartDate=1984-10-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>1984年年末，珍妮与儿时的伙伴、同事，R&B歌手{{tsl|en|James DeBarge|James DeBarge}}私奔。但是这段婚姻1985年就宣告终止。<ref>{{Citation|last=Smith|first=Jessie Carney|title = Notable Black American women, Volume 2 | publisher=[[Gale_(Cengage)|Gale]]|year=1996|page=324|isbn=978-0-8103-9177-2}}</ref>1985年，珍妮和姐姐[[拉托亞·傑克森|拉托亞]]一起参加了{{tsl|en|Yamaha Music Festival|雅马哈世界歌谣祭}}，并获得银奖以及最佳歌曲奖。

=== 1986–1988：《控制》 ===
在发行完《{{tsl|en|Dream Street (Janet Jackson album)|Dream Street}}》之后，珍妮决定将自己的演艺事业脱离她的家族。她后来评论道：「我只是想离开我的家庭，摆脱我父亲的控制。而告诉我父亲说我不想再和他一起工作了，正是我人生当中所做的最艰难的事情之一。(I just wanted to get out of the house, get out from under my father, which was one of the most difficult things that I had to do, telling him that I didn't want to work with him again.)」<ref name="Saunders"/>A&M唱片公司的主管John McClain随后雇佣了制作人Jimmy Jam与Terry Lewis与珍妮合作。经过6周的努力，他们完成了珍妮的第三张录音室专辑《[[控制_(珍娜傑克森專輯)|控制]]》<ref name="cohen">{{Citation | last = Cohen | first = Jonathan | title = Billboard Feature: Janet Jackson: Still In Control | url = http://www.allbusiness.com/retail-trade/miscellaneous-retail-retail-stores-not/4614593-1.html | work = Billboard | date = 1999-12-15 | accessdate = 2010-09-06 | archive-date = 2011-01-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110110093834/http://www.allbusiness.com/retail-trade/miscellaneous-retail-retail-stores-not/4614593-1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>珍妮回忆到，在她录制这张专辑的时候，她在[[明尼阿波利斯|明尼阿波利斯]]的酒店外面被一群男人威胁，她描述当时的情形说：「当一群男人开始跟踪我时，我觉得危险向我袭来。但是我并没有退缩或者寻求Jimmy和Terry的保护，我鼓足了勇气反抗，并让他们退缩了。这也是我后来创作《[[下流_(珍娜傑克森歌曲)|Nasty]]》与《[[看你做的好事|What Have You Done for Me Lately]]》这两首歌的灵感所在，他们都出自于一种自我防卫的意识。」<ref name="Sexual Healing"/>

虽然Jam和Lewis也希望能吸引各族群的注意力以及视听口味，但他们的首要目标仍然是将珍妮塑造成一个典型的美国黑人女歌手。<ref name="She's a rebel">{{Citation | last = Gaar | first = Gillian G. | title = She's a rebel: the history of women in rock & roll | publisher=Seal Press | year = 2002 | pages = 323–325 | isbn = 1-58005-078-6}}</ref>Jam评论这张专辑时说道：我们希望创作一张迎合每一个美国黑人家庭的唱片，这也是我们一直以来的目标。<ref name="She's a rebel"/>1986年2月，专辑《[[控制_(珍娜傑克森專輯)|控制]]》上市发行，获得了爆炸性的成功，并在同年7月以单周20万张的销量在[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|告示牌專輯榜]]中奪冠。<ref name="Billboard Album peaks"/><ref>{{Citation|url=http://books.google.com/?id=B_38rmDqlLQC&pg=PA50&dq=janet+jackson+200,000#v=onepage&q=janet%20jackson%20200%2C000&f=false |title=Janet Jackson's Control |publisher=[[Spin_(雜誌)|Spin]] |accessdate=2010-09-30|date=1987-01}}</ref>《洛杉矶时报》的评论家Connie Johnson写道：「虽然歌手仍然是一个青少年，但是却有非常坚定、冷静以及成熟的观点。她清晰的剖析了当今青少年的青涩岁月，并用音乐的肌腱将他们串联起来。」<ref>{{citation|last=Johnson|first=Connie|title=Jackson Jive|newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|page=78|date=1986-02-23|issn=0458-3035}}</ref>《新闻周刊》评论这张专辑时认为这张专辑”结合了[[Patti_LaBelle|Patti LaBelle]]和[[惠特妮·休斯顿|惠妮·休斯頓]]（Whitney Houston）的伤感情歌和华丽编曲效果。“<ref>{{Citation | title = Singer Janet Jackson | volume= 108 | issue = 3 | page = 61 | newspaper=[[Newsweek|Newsweek]]| date = 1986-07-21| issn = 0028-9604}}</ref>Rob Hoerburger在《[[滚石杂志|滚石杂志]]》上评价《Control》这张专辑比[[戴安娜·罗斯|黛安娜·羅絲]]（Diana Ross）近5年来的所有专辑都要出色，而且将珍妮形容为年轻的[[:en:Donna_Summer|Donna Summer]]。并断言她将不会固步自封而会以自己的脚步不断的超越。<ref>{{Citation | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/janetjackson/albums/album/321531/review/5944692/control | title = Janet Jackson: Control: Music Reviews: Rolling Stone | last = Hoerburger | first = Rob | work = Rolling Stone | date = 1986-04-24 | accessdate = 2010-09-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080430054634/http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/janetjackson/albums/album/321531/review/5944692/control | archivedate = 2008-04-30 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>

专辑中的五支单曲《[[看你做的好事|What Have You Done for Me Lately]]》、《[[下流_(珍娜傑克森歌曲)|Nasty]]》、《[[每當想起你|When I Think of You]]》、《[[控制_(珍娜傑克森歌曲)|Control]]》和《[[慢慢來|Let's Wait Awhile]]》均打入了[[公告牌百强单曲榜|告示牌單曲榜]]前五名。<ref name="singles peaks">{{Citation |url=http://www.billboard.com/#/artist/janet-jackson/chart-history/4899 |title=Artist Chart History – Janet Jackson |work=Billboard |accessdate=2010-09-06 |archive-date=2012-07-28 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120728/http://www.billboard.com/%23/artist/eddie-murphy/chart-history/1173?f=305&g=Albums#/artist/janet-jackson/chart-history/4899 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而单曲《When I Think of You》也成为珍妮的第一支全美冠军单曲。此外《The Pleasure Principle》也打入了20强，最高排名第十四位。<ref name="singles peaks"/>专辑《Control》中的大多数音乐录影带都由当时尚名不见经传的[[寶拉·阿巴杜|寶拉·阿巴杜]]（Paula Abdul）操刀。公告牌杂志评论道：「（珍妮·杰克逊）的音乐录音带也给[[MTV|MTV]]电视台带来了巨大的影响，并使得这个原本只是一个普通的摇滚乐音乐频道转变成了时尚音乐的新指标。」<ref name="cohen"/>

《Control》在美国获得了[[RIAA|RIAA]]五白金的销量认证，并在全世界创造了超过一千四百万张的销量记录。<ref name="PR"/><ref name="cert">{{Citation | title = Gold & Platinum | publisher = Recording Industry Association of America | year = 1958–2009 | url = http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?resultpage=1&table=SEARCH_RESULTS&action=&title=&artist=Janet%20Jackson&format=ALBUM&debutLP=&category=&sex=&releaseDate=&requestNo=&type=&level=&label=&company=&certificationDate=&awardDescription=&catalogNo=&aSex=&rec_id=&charField=&gold=&platinum=&multiPlat=&level2=&certDate=&album=&id=&after=&before=&startMonth=1&endMonth=1&startYear=1958&endYear=2009&sort=Artist&perPage=25 | accessdate = 2009-10-07 | archive-date = 2013-09-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130914145208/http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?resultpage=1&table=SEARCH_RESULTS&action=&title=&artist=Janet%20Jackson&format=ALBUM&debutLP=&category=&sex=&releaseDate=&requestNo=&type=&level=&label=&company=&certificationDate=&awardDescription=&catalogNo=&aSex=&rec_id=&charField=&gold=&platinum=&multiPlat=&level2=&certDate=&album=&id=&after=&before=&startMonth=1&endMonth=1&startYear=1958&endYear=2009&sort=Artist&perPage=25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>而专辑在[[全美音乐奖|全美音乐奖]]上所创的十二项提名的记录至今无人可破，并获得四项大奖。专辑也获得了[[葛莱美奖|葛莱美奖]]年度最佳专辑提名的肯定。<ref>{{citation|last=Smith|first=Kathleen|title=American Music Awards tonight to honor Presley posthumously|newspaper=[[St._Petersburg_Times|St. Petersburg Times]]|page=7.D|date=1987-01-26}}</ref><ref>{{citation|title=Travis tops music award winners|newspaper=[[Houston_Chronicle|Houston Chronicle]]|date=1988-01-26|page=1|issn=1074-7109}}</ref><ref>{{Citation | last1 = Hamlin | first1 = Jesse | title = Graced With a Grammy / Paul Simon wins award for top album | page = 48 | newspaper=[[San_Francisco_Chronicle|San Francisco Chronicle]] | date = 1987-02-25 }}</ref>

=== 1989–1992：《珍妮·杰克逊的节奏王国 1814》 ===
1989年9月，珍妮发行了她自己的第四张录音室专辑《[[Janet_Jackson's_Rhythm_Nation_1814|節奏國度]]》。虽然A&M唱片公司希望延续上一张专辑《Control》的风格，但是她本人却坚持在新专辑中添加更多的现实信息，用她的歌曲来表达自己对爱情和两性关系的观点。<ref>{{Citation | last1 = Cocks | first1 = Jay | title = Dancing on the charts | volume = 135 | issue = 22 | page = 87 | newspaper=TIME | date = 1990-05-28 | issn = 0040-781X}}</ref>她说：“我并不幼稚，我知道一张专辑或者一首歌曲不能改变世界，我只希望我的音乐和我的舞蹈能够吸引住观众的注意力，并保持足够长的时间，让他们能听出歌词中我想表达的东西。”<ref>{{Citation |last1 =Graham | first1 = Jefferson | title = Janet in command; Jackson rules her own `Nation'; Highlights of a rhythmic life | page = 01.D | newspaper=[[今日美国|今日美国]] | date = 1989-12-15 }}</ref>专辑的制作人Jimmy Jam在接受《波士顿环球报》采访时说：“我们总有一台电视机是开着的，通常都转到[[CNN|CNN]]频道...我想专辑中现实题材的歌曲像《[[節奏國度|Rhythm Nation]]》、《State of the World》和《The Knowledge》的创作灵感都来源于此。<ref>{{Citation| last1 = Morse | first1 = Steve | title = Changing Her Tune Janet Jackson's New Conscience | page = 30 | newspaper=波士顿环球报 | date = 1989-11-20 }}</ref>《滚石杂志》的Vince Aletti在文章中称：“他观察到珍妮·杰克逊所关注的议题已经从个人情感转向了整个社会中所存在的问题：不公正、不文明、犯罪、毒品——包罗万象。”<ref>{{Citation | last = Aletti | first = Vince | title = Rhythm Nation 1814: Janet Jackson: Review: Rolling Stone | work = Rolling Stone | date = 1998-10-19 | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/janetjackson/albums/album/182747/review/5943659/rhythm_nation_1814 | accessdate = 2010-09-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080430054629/http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/janetjackson/albums/album/182747/review/5943659/rhythm_nation_1814 | archivedate = 2008-04-30 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>

这张[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|告示牌專輯榜]]冠军专辑最终获得了美国六白金的销量认证，在全球已售出了超过1400万张。<ref name="PR"/><ref name="Billboard Album peaks"/><ref name="cert"/>
而这张专辑也成为音乐史上唯一一张连续三年均产生[[公告牌百强单曲榜|告示牌單曲榜]]冠军单曲的专辑——1989年4週冠軍的《[[Miss_You_Much|Miss You Much]]》、1990年3週冠軍的《[[Escapade_(歌曲)|Escapade]]》和1週冠軍的《[[Black_Cat_(歌曲)|Black Cat]]》，以及1991年1週冠軍的《[[Love_Will_Never_Do_(Without_You)|Love Will Never Do (Without You)]]》。与此同时也是历史上唯一一张7支单曲均打入单曲榜前五位的专辑。<ref>{{Citation |url=http://djtoma.blogspot.com/2009/01/janet-jackson-rhythm-nation-1814.html |title=VINTAGE VYBZ DOWNUNDER: Janet Jackson - Rhythm Nation 1814 |publisher=djtoma.blogspot.com |date=2009-01-12 |accessdate=2010-09-06 |archive-date=2011-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708033218/http://djtoma.blogspot.com/2009/01/janet-jackson-rhythm-nation-1814.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Dowell">{{Citation| last = Dowell | first = Dowell | coauthors = Kim Jones | title = Heritage Signature Entertainment Memorabilia Auction #622 | publisher=Heritage Capital Corporation | year = 2006 | page = 139 | isbn = 1-59967-036-4}}</ref>为专辑所摄制的音乐录影带《[[節奏國度|Rhythm Nation]]》也赢得了1989年[[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]最佳长篇音乐录影带奖。<ref name="Grammy Awards">{{Citation | title = Grammy Winners Search | publisher = The Recording Academy | year = 2008 | url = http://www.grammy.com/GRAMMY_Awards/Winners/Results.aspx?title=&winner=janet%20jackson&year=0&genreID=0&hp=1 | accessdate = 2008-07-27 | archive-date = 2009-01-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090111110127/http://www.grammy.com/GRAMMY_Awards/Winners/Results.aspx?title=&winner=janet%20jackson&year=0&genreID=0&hp=1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>《公告牌》杂志也宣布《節奏國度》是1990年销量最高的专辑。<ref>{{Citation |last=Macdonald |first=Patrick |title = Ringing In 1991: Northwest Top 10 Video Count-Down | page = 8 | newspaper=[[The_Seattle_Times|The Seattle Times]] | date = 1990-12-28 }}</ref><ref>{{Citation | last1 = Anderson | first1 = Susan | title = Chronicle | page = 7 | newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | date = 1990-11-28 | isbn = 0-8118-6207-0 | issn = 0362-4331}}</ref>依托这张专辑而展开的名为{{tsl|en|Rhythm Nation World Tour|Rhythm Nation World Tour}}的珍妮首次世界巡演，也是唱片歌手首次世界巡回演唱会中成绩最佳的。<ref>{{Citation| last = Jaynes | first = Gerald David | title = Encyclopedia of African American Society | publisher=[[SAGE_Publications|SAGE Publications]] | year = 2005 | page = 565 | isbn = 0-7619-2764-6}}</ref>当珍妮开始自己的巡演之后，她开始意识到自己对流行音乐的影响。《旧金山纪事报》的{{tsl|en|Joel Selvin|Joel Selvin}}评论道：这个23岁的年轻人刷新了一系列的记录，成为MTV的新指标，以及整个国家青少年少女的国民偶像。”而时任{{tsl|en|United Negro College Fund|黑人学院联合基金}}副总裁的William Allen则对《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》说：“珍妮·杰克逊是所有青少年应该学习的榜样，她本人通过专辑《節奏國度》中的歌词，向这个国家的青少年传递了正面的信息。”<ref>{{Citation |last=Selvin |first=Joel |title = Just Wholesome Glitz From Janet | page = F1 | newspaper=[[San_Francisco_Chronicle|San Francisco Chronicle]] | date = 1990-04-30 }}</ref><ref>{{Citation |title = Names In The News Janet Jackson Benefit Concert | page = 9 | newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | date = 1990-02-05 |issn=0458-3035}}</ref>她也与黑人学院联合基金共同设立了"节奏王国奖学金"，并从演唱会的收入中捐助此项以及其他教育计划，总计金额超过50万美元。<ref>{{Citation |title = Janet Jackson Ends 'Rhythm Nation' Tour, Donates over $1/2 Million to Fund Education Projects | page = 56 | newspaper=[[Jet_(magazine)|Jet]] |volume=79|issue=13| date = 1991-01-14|issn=0021-5996}}</ref><ref>{{Citation |title = Janet Combines Talent and Appeal for UNCF | page = B–3 | newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Sentinel|Los Angeles Sentinel]] | date = 1994-03-03|issn=0890-4340}}</ref>而根据2000年英国Routledge出版社出版的《Routledge世界妇女百科全书：全球妇女议题及知识》中记载，珍妮·杰克逊凭借在当时的成功，使她成为世界上最成功的音乐人之一，能与她的兄长[[麥可·傑克森|麥可·傑克森]]、[[瑪丹娜|瑪丹娜]]以及[[蒂娜·特纳|蒂娜·透娜]]并肩。<ref name="Routledge">{{Citation| last = Kramarae | first = Cheris | coauthors = Dale Spender | title = Routledge International Encyclopedia of Women: Global Women's Issues and Knowledge | publisher=[[Routledge|Routledge]] | year = 2000 | page = 1408 | isbn = 0-415-92091-4}}</ref>

随着《[[Janet_Jackson's_Rhythm_Nation_1814|節奏國度]]》的发行，珍妮·杰克逊与A&M唱片公司正式约满，顿时成为各大唱片公司追逐邀约的对象。1991年，在[[维京唱片|维京唱片]]的老板[[理查德·布蘭森|理查德·布兰森]]亲自接洽下，她与该厂牌签下了一纸唱片合约。<ref name="Jackson's Double Play">{{Citation | last1 = Wild | first1 = David | title = Jackson's Double Play | issue = 657 | page = 18 | newspaper=Rolling Stone | date = 1993-05-27 | issn = 0035-791X}}</ref><ref name="Robert Hilburn">{{Citation | last= Hilburn | first= Robert | title= I Think I've Finally Grown Up | newspaper=[[Newsday|Newsday]] | page=10 | year=1993 | date= 1994-06-27}}</ref><ref name="virgin contract">{{Citation | last1 = Goldberg | first1 = M. | title = The Jacksons score big | page = 32 | newspaper=Rolling Stone | date = 1991-05-02 | issn = 0035-791X}}</ref>虽然合同的具体金额没有公布，但是业内人士大致预计合同金额约在3200万美元至5000万美元之间，这也使她成为当时音乐史上最值钱的音乐人。这个记录随后被她的哥哥[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔·杰克逊]]与[[索尼音乐娱乐|Sony]]公司6500万美元的续约合同所打破。<ref name="multimillion">{{citation|title=The Biggest Brother-Sister Stars in Show Business History|newspaper=[[Ebony_(magazine)|Ebony]]|volume=46|issue=10|page=40|issn=0012-9011}}</ref>黑人杂志《{{tsl|en|Ebony (magazine)|Ebony}}》评价道：”任何人和团体，都没有像近期分别签下价值数千万唱片美元合约迈克尔和珍妮兄妹这样来震撼这个世界的娱乐界。虽然他们有众多的模仿者，但是却极少有能像他们这样令人惊叹的风格和风度的出现。“<ref name="multimillion"/>珍妮的时尚指标的地位也进一步的稳固，”在她超过200万歌迷参与的世界巡演中，无数的少女模仿她穿起了特质的黑色军装式样的夹克，黑色紧身裤和白色大衬衫。“<ref name="multimillion"/>同年，她与她长期的伙伴、舞蹈家、作曲家、导演{{tsl|en|René Elizondo, Jr.|René Elizondo, Jr.}}秘密结婚。<ref name="Gordinier"/>1992年初，她与著名歌手[[路德·范德鲁斯|路德·范德鲁斯]]合作,为电影《{{tsl|en|Mo' Money (soundtrack)|过路财神}}》演唱了歌曲《{{tsl|en|The Best Things in Life Are Free|The Best Things in Life Are Free}}》。

=== 1993–1996：《珍妮》， 《写诗的贾斯廷斯》、登上《滾石》杂志封面和《十年精选 1986/1996》 ===
1992年8月，当珍妮·杰克逊完成了自己首部担纲主演的电影《{{tsl|en|Poetic Justice (film)|写诗的贾斯廷斯}}》(Poetic Justice)的拍摄工作之后，她开始着手计划推出自己在维京旗下的首张专辑。专辑於1992年9月开始制作，并於次年一季度完成。1993年5月，珍妮推出了自己第五张录音室专辑《[[Janet_(專輯)|珍娜]]》，专辑一上市就获得巨大的成功，迅速登上了[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|告示牌專輯榜]]的榜首。<ref name="Billboard Album peaks"/>而关于专辑的名称，珍妮解释道：“当然，很多人肯定会觉得我是依靠着我的姓氏来成功的...这就是我只把我自己的名字放在封面上的缘故。也因此，我从来没有让我的哥哥们来帮我创作和制作音乐。“<ref>{{Citation | last=Gundersen | first=Edna | title=All About Janet | newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] | page=1 | date= 1994-02-18}}</ref>《公告牌》杂志的Larry Flick评论道：”珍妮在这张专辑中将自己的音乐领域进一步的扩大，[[浩室音乐|浩室音乐]]、[[:en:Swing_music|摇摆舞乐]]、[[嘻哈|嘻哈]]、[[摇滚|摇滚]]以及{{tsl|en|List of Caribbean music genres|加勒比海风格}}的音乐元素与珍妮招牌式的电台[[放克|放克]]音乐充分结合在了一起。“<ref>{{Citation | last=Flick | first=Larry | title=Janet makes definitive statement | newspaper=billboard | page=17 | date=1993-05-22}}</ref>而《滚石》杂志则写道：”作为美国黑人”皇室家族“的小公主，珍妮所做的一切事情都是重要的。无论是宣布将自己掌握自己的生活，摆脱别人的”控制“（《Control》1986），还是率领一个舞蹈军团与这个社会中所存在的问题对抗(《節奏國度》1989)，她总是充满了影响力。而当她在自己的新专辑《[[Janet_(專輯)|珍娜]]》中散发自己无穷的性感和成熟魅力时，这同样也是文化史上重要的一刻。“<ref>{{citation |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/janetjackson/albums/album/182126/review/6067467/janet |title=Janet Jackson: Janet : Music Reviews |work=Rolling Stone |accessdate=2010-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080502093343/http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/janetjackson/albums/album/182126/review/6067467/janet |archivedate=2008-05-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>2004年出版的《新滚石专辑指南》中提到，专辑中的8週冠军单曲并获得1994年[[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]最佳R&B歌曲奖的《[[That's_the_Way_Love_Goes_(Janet_Jackson_song)|That's the Way Love Goes]]》、2週冠軍的《[[Again_(珍納·積遜單曲)|Again]]》以及其他top10单曲如《[[:en:If_(Janet_Jackson_song)|If]]》、《[[:en:Because_of_Love|Because of Love]]》、《[[:en:You_Want_This|You Want This]]》和《[[:en:Any_Time,_Any_Place|Any Time, Any Place]]》都富含了一种”长大成人之后的欲望“。<ref name="Grammy Awards"/><ref>{{Citation| last =Brackett | first =Nathan| title = The New Rolling Stone Album Guide | publisher=Simon and Schuster | year = 2004 | page = 411 | isbn = 0-7432-0169-8 | coauthors= Christian David Hoard, Christian Hoard}}</ref>《珍娜》这张专辑最终由RIAA认证为6白金专辑，在全世界范围内也销售了超过2000万张。<ref name="cert"/><ref>{{citation |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2008/01/22/2143685.htm |title=Janet Jackson set for return to form |publisher=[[ABC_News|ABC News]] |date=2008-01-22 |accessdate=2009-05-05 |archive-date=2012-07-28 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69Uhb5X5Q?url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2008-01-22/janet-jackson-set-for-return-to-form/1019448 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1993年，珍妮第一次担任主演的电影《{{tsl|en|Poetic Justice (film)|写诗的贾斯廷斯}}》(Poetic Justice)上映。《滚石》杂志评论珍妮的表演虽然青涩但“作为首次领衔还算有趣”而《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》则称她的表演“略显古怪”。<ref>{{Citation | title = Poetic Justice | work = Rolling Stone | date = 2000-12-08 | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/reviews/movie/5947325/review/5947326/poetic_justice | accessdate = 2008-06-13 | archive-date = 2010-04-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100409203949/http://www.rollingstone.com/reviews/movie/5947325/review/5947326/poetic_justice | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Citation | last = Howe | first = Desson | title = Poetic Justice | work = The Washington Post | date = 1993-07-23 | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/poeticjusticerhowe_a0afdf.htm | accessdate = 2008-06-13 | archive-date = 2011-06-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110629020612/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/poeticjusticerhowe_a0afdf.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>其他的评论也相对负面，《娱乐周刊》的Owen Gleiberman称：“她并不是一个称职的女演员，她塑造的形象除了像丘比洋娃娃那样有张可爱的塑料面具之外，个性上毫无棱角。”<ref>{{citation|last=Gleiberman|first=Owen|title=Poetic Justice Movie Review|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,307326,00.html|newspaper=Entertainment Weekly|year=1993|accessdate=2009-10-02|archive-date=2009-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091222193058/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,307326,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>尽管如此，她为电影配唱的抒情歌曲《[[Again_(珍納·積遜單曲)|Again]]》却在次年为她带来了一座[[金球奖|金球奖]]最佳电影原创歌曲奖以及一项[[奥斯卡奖|奥斯卡奖]]最佳电影原创歌曲奖提名。<ref>{{Citation | last= Biddle | first= Frederic M. | title= Fashion and fame team on Oscar night | newspaper=The Boston Globe | page=61 | date= 1994-03-22}}</ref><ref>{{citation|title=HFPA - Awards Search|url=http://www.goldenglobes.org/browse/member/30554|publisher=[[Hollywood_Foreign_Press_Association|Hollywood Foreign Press Association]]|year=1993|accessdate=2010-09-18|archive-date=2010-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100713152201/http://www.goldenglobes.org/browse/member/30554|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[File:Janetrollingstone.jpg|thumb]]封面]]
1993年9月，珍妮登上了《滚石》杂志的封面。只穿了一条低腰牛仔裤的珍妮上半身全裸，只由一个男人从背后伸手盖住了她的双峰。这张由传奇时尚摄影师{{tsl|en|Patrick Demarchelier|Patrick Demarchelier}}亲自操刀的摄影作品，本身也是《珍娜》专辑封面照片的完整版。而那个身藏珍妮背后的男人一直也是娱乐界的一大问号之一。直至近年，才有相关知情人士透露这位男子是当时与珍妮秘密结婚的René Elizondo, Jr.。<ref>{{Citation | title = Janet Jackson | work = Rolling Stone | date = 2004-09-30 | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/news/story/6478137/janet_jackson | accessdate = 2008-07-23 | archive-date = 2012-06-26 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/68iUDeAEB?url=http://www.rollingstone.com/news | dead-url = no }}</ref>《[[温哥华太阳报|温哥华太阳报]]》的Sonia Murray随后报道说：“杰克逊，27岁，继续确立了她时尚偶像和性感符号的形象，而《滚石》杂志的这张杰克逊封面...可谓是今年最知名以及最震撼的杂志封面。“<ref>{{Citation | last1 = Murray | first1 = Sonia | title = Janet: The Queen of Pop: Michael could lose his crown to his hot little sister | page = C1 | newspaper=[[The_Vancouver_Sun|The Vancouver Sun]]| date = 1994-02-03| issn = 0832-1299}}</ref>而作家{{tsl|en|David Ritz|David Ritz}}则把她与[[马文·盖伊|马文·盖伊]]相比较，认为就像当年马文·盖伊从专辑《[[What's_Going_On|What's Going On]]》向《[[:en:Let's_Get_It_On|Let's Get It On]]》寻求突破一样，是一种自我意识的觉醒。而珍妮则用《節奏國度》向《珍娜》的转变，向世人发布了自己性解放的宣言。”<ref name="Sexual Healing">{{Citation | last1 = Ritz | first1 = David | title = Sexual healing | issue = 665 | page = 38 | newspaper=Rolling Stone | date = 1993-09-16 | issn = 0035-791X}}</ref>她随即展开的第二次世界巡回演唱会{{tsl|en|Janet World Tour|Janet World Tour}}也取得了巨大的成功。《旧金山纪事报》的Michael Snyder评价珍妮的舞台表演突破了传统意义上歌手体育馆演唱会与剧场狂想曲之间的界限。<ref name="Michael Snyder">{{Citation | last=Snyder | first=Michael | title=Janet Jackson Makes All The Right Moves / Singer brings extravaganza to San Jose | newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle | page=C1 | date=1994-02-18}}</ref>

这段时间，她的兄长迈克尔正深陷于{{tsl|en|1993 child sexual abuse accusations against Michael Jackson|猥亵儿童丑闻}}之中，虽然迈克尔否认了全部的罪行，但是舆论界却紧盯他不放。<ref>{{Citation |last1=Corliss |first1=Richard |last2=Sachs |first2=Andrea |title=Society: Who's Bad? An age of innocence may be at an end as Michael Jackson, the Peter Pan of pop, confronts accusations that he sexually abused one of his young friends | newspaper=TIME| page=54 | date=1993-09-06}}</ref>而珍妮也给予了她哥哥巨大的支持。她公开否认他们的姐姐La Toya在1991年出版的自传《{{tsl|en|La Toya: Growing Up in the Jackson Family|La Toya: Growing Up in the Jackson Family}}》中对他们的父母从小虐待他们的指控，<ref name="Robert Hilburn"/>并在接受《Ebony》杂志采访时宣称，她认为她的姐姐将自己封闭起来，和她的家族已经疏远了，并沉迷于自己的幻想之中。这主要是归咎於她的丈夫{{tsl|en|Jack Gordon (entertainment manager)|Jack Gordon}}对她进行长期洗脑的结果。<ref name="Latoya">{{Citation |last1=Norment|first1=Lynn |title=Grown-up Janet Jackson talks about racism, sensuality and the Jackson family | newspaper=Ebony|volume=48|issue=11| page=36 | date=September 1993|issn=0012-9011}}</ref>与此同时，她也批评她兄长杰梅因在1991年发表的单曲《Word to the Badd》中对迈克尔的抨击。<ref name="Latoya"/>1994年11月，她和迈克尔一起演唱了歌曲《{{tsl|en|Scream/Childhood|Scream}}》,这支迈克尔1995年的专辑《[[HIStory:_Past,_Present_and_Future,_Book_I|HIStory]]》的首波主打单曲描述了舆论界因猥亵儿童丑闻给他们的家族所带来的巨大压力和痛苦。<ref name="TCI">{{Citation |last=Boepple |first= Leanne |title = Scream: space odyssey Jackson-style.(video production; Michael and Janet Jackson video) | page = 52 |volume=29 | newspaper=Theatre Crafts International | date = 1995-11-01 |issn=1063-9497}}</ref>这支单曲首周进榜排名第五，成为乐坛史上首支发行第一周就荣登Top5的单曲。而单曲的音乐录影带也被吉尼斯世界纪录评定为”史上耗资最巨大的音乐录影带“，成本逾700万美元之巨。这也让这对兄妹获得了1995年格莱美奖最佳音乐录影带短篇奖。<ref name="Grammy Awards"/>

1995年10月，珍妮推出了自己的首张新歌+精选专辑《{{tsl|en|Design of a Decade 1986/1996|Design of a Decade 1986/1996}}》,这张由维京与A&M唱片公司共同制作的专辑在专辑榜上首周排名第四，并最高排名第三。<ref name="Billboard Album peaks"/>专辑中的主打单曲《{{tsl|en|Runaway (Janet Jackson song)|Runaway}}》则是史上第一支一发行首周便打入单曲榜Top10的单曲，最高排名第三。<ref>{{citation|first=Bronson |last=Fred |title=Janet Jackson Has Done It Again |url=http://books.google.com/?id=6Q0EAAAAMBAJ&printsec=frontcover |work=Billboard |publisher=[[Nielsen_Company|Nielsen Business Media, Inc.]] |page=96 |date=September 16, 1995 |accessdate=2010-04-17}}</ref><ref>{{Citation| title = Design of a Decade 1986/1996 > Charts & Awards > Billboard Singles | publisher=Allmusic | year = 2006 | url = {{Allmusic|class=album|id=r224159|pure_url=yes}}| accessdate = 2008-07-20}}</ref>《Design of a Decade 1986/1996》最终由RIAA认证为双白金专辑，全世界的累积销量也打到了400万张。<ref name="cert"/><ref>{{Citation |last=Jones|first=Steve| title=Janet digs deep Jackson confronts knotty issues with introspective 'Velvet Rope' | newspaper=USA TODAY | page=1.D | date=1997-10-07|issn=0734-7456}}</ref>通过这张专辑，珍妮进一步确立了自己在乐坛的地位，《波士顿环球报》的Steve Morse写道：”说起这个世界上最有影响力的女性精英时，你会不由的想到珍妮·杰克逊、{{tsl|en|Bonnie Raitt|Bonnie Raitt}}、[[瑪丹娜|瑪丹娜]]和[[小野洋子|小野洋子]]，她们的影响力不可估量。你现在还能说珍妮没有达到她的哥哥迈克尔那样的高度吗？“<ref>{{citation|last=Morse|first=Steve|title=Pure pop for power women Janet Jackson, Bonnie Raitt, Yoko Ono and Madonna flex their musical muscle|newspaper=''The Boston Globe''|page=51|date=1995-11-03|issn=0743-1791}}</ref>精选集的推出完成了珍妮与维京的唱片合约，这又使得她成为唱片工业各大巨头争相招揽的巨星。1996年1月，珍妮与维京唱片续约，签约费高达8000万美元。<ref name="80 million">{{Citation | title=Janet Jackson Hits Big; $80 Million Record Deal | newspaper=Newsday | page=A02 | date=1996-01-13}}</ref>这张合约使得她又一次成为音乐史上酬劳最高的艺人。甚至高于她的兄长迈克尔6500万美元的签约费和[[瑪丹娜|瑪丹娜]]6000万美元的合同。十年之内，珍妮两次创造了历史。<ref>They don't call it jackpot for nothing. After much speculation, Janet Jackson, 29, clinched a reported four-album, $80 million deal with Virgin Records, making her the music industry's highest-paid performer (over brother Michael and Madonna, who each got $60 million deals in the early '90s) {{Citation |last1=Davidson |first1=Casey | title=News & Notes | newspaper=Entertainment Weekly | page=15 | date=1996-01-26}}</ref><ref>{{Citation |last1= Farley |first1=Christopher John |last2= Thigpen |first2=David E. |last3= Ressner |first3=Jeffrey | title=Business: Are they worth all that cash? Janet Jackson's record-breaking $80 million contract could set off a new wave of pop-music megadeals | newspaper=TIME| page=54 | date=1996-01-29}}</ref><ref>Rock band [[R.E.M.|R.E.M.]] later signed an $80 million dollar recording contract with [[Warner_Bros._Records|Warner Bros. Records]] in August 1996; sources compared the group's record deal with Jackson's contract, but quoted her earning a comparatively lower estimate of $70 million dollars. {{Citation | title=R.E.M. Signs $80M Deal | newspaper=Newsday | date=1996-08-26}}</ref>

=== 1997–1999：《华丽的冒险》 ===
经过两年的筹备与制作，珍妮发行了自己的第六张录音室专辑《[[The_Velvet_Rope|華麗的冒險]]》,而在这段时间里，珍妮也一直饱受忧郁症与焦虑症的困扰。<ref name="Saunders"/>《波士顿环球报》的Michael Saunders认为这张专辑本身就是珍妮与忧郁症搏斗过程的写照，并形容这张专辑是”一次严格的自省，也是一次用音乐来记录的自我发现的旅程“<ref name="Saunders"/>而《華麗的冒險》也将[[施虐与受虐|施虐与受虐]]与珍妮的音乐相结合。著名乐评杂志《[[:en:Slant_Magazine|偏锋]]》的Eric Henderson写道：”《[[The_Velvet_Rope|華麗的冒險]]》是一张充满黑色元素的杰作，加上内页中的铁链和皮鞭，没有什么东西能比情感上的赤裸更加性感了。“<ref>{{Citation| last = Henderson| first = Eric| title = Slant Magazine Music Review: Janet Jackson: The Velvet Rope| work = Slant| year = 2006| url = http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/music_review.asp?ID=973| accessdate = 2008-07-20| archive-date = 2007-01-09| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070109025128/http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/music_review.asp?ID=973| dead-url = no}}</ref>《公告牌》的Larry Flick称这张专辑是”今年美国乐坛最好的专辑，也比她之前的五张专辑更加出色。“<ref>{{citation|last=Flick|first=Larry|title=The Year in Music|newspaper=Billboard|volume=109|issue=52|page=16|date=1998-12-03|issn=0006-2510}}</ref>专辑於1997年10月出版，首次进榜即登上[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|告示牌專輯榜]]冠军。<ref name="Billboard Album peaks"/>1997年8月，专辑的首波主打单曲《[[:en:Got_'til_It's_Gone|Got 'til It's Gone]]》通过电台公开，在公告牌电台榜上最高排名12。<ref>{{Citation| title = Janet Jackson: Charts & Awards: Billboard Singles | publisher=Allmusic | year = 1997 | url = {{Allmusic|class=artist|id=p4572|pure_url=yes}} | accessdate = 2010-09-09}}</ref>
这张单曲节选了一小段[[Joni_Mitchell|Joni Mitchell]]创作的名曲《{{tsl|en|Big Yellow Taxi|Big Yellow Taxi}}》中的一小段旋律，并由饶舌歌手{{tsl|en|Q-Tip (rapper)|Q-Tip}}共同演绎。《Got 'til It's Gone》的音乐录影带也获得了1997年[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]最佳短篇音乐录影带奖。<ref name="Grammy Awards"/>专辑的第二首单曲《[[Together_Again_(珍娜·傑克森單曲)|Together Again]]》取得了空前的成功，成为珍妮第八首[[公告牌百强单曲榜|告示牌單曲榜]]冠军单曲。这一成绩也使她和[[Elton_John|Elton John]]、[[Diana_Ross|Diana Ross]]和[[The_Rolling_Stones|The Rolling Stones]]等传奇音乐人打平。<ref name="Jacksons Number Ones">{{Citation| last = Halstead | first = Craig | coauthors = Craig Halstead, Chris Cadman | title = Jacksons Number Ones | publisher=Authors On Line | year = 2003 | pages = 28, 120 | isbn = 0-7552-0098-5}}</ref>专辑连续46周保持在美国单曲榜榜单之内，在英国单曲榜中也连续上榜了19周。<ref name="Jacksons Number Ones"/>出自专辑的另一首单曲《[[我好寂寞_(珍娜·傑克森單曲)|I Get Lonely]]》也打入了美国单曲榜Top3。<ref name="singles peaks"/>专辑在世界范围内总共销售了1000万张，而在美国则获得了RIAA三白金的销量认证。<ref name="PR"/><ref name="cert"/>

珍妮将单曲《Together Again》的部分利润捐献给了{{tsl|en|AmfAR|美国艾滋病研究基金会}}。<ref name="Jacksons Number Ones"/> 《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的Neil McCormick评论道：”（珍妮）从这张专辑开始成为了一名真正意义上的同性恋偶像，在《Together Again》这首反艾滋病歌曲中的表现不由的让人想起了反艾滋的艺能界先驱Diana Ross，而在鼓励人们勇敢面对自己性取向的歌曲《Free Xone》则是一首对同性恋的赞歌，而[[罗德·斯图尔特|罗德·斯图尔特]]的经典老歌《{{tsl|en|Tonight's the Night (Gonna Be Alright)|'Tonight's the Night'}}》则由珍妮诠释的充满了女同性恋的魅力。“<ref name="McCormick">{{Citation |last=McCormick |first=Neil | title=The Arts: Give her enough rope ... Reviews Rock CDs | newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] | page=11| date=1997-10-18}}</ref>《滚石》杂志则认为《Free Xone》是整张专辑中最优秀的歌曲，形容它是一首优秀的反同性恋恐惧症歌曲，从[[王子_(音樂家)|王子]]般的曲风完美的过渡到Archie Bell and the Drells的《Tighten Up》的吉他片段，每一个细微的部分都透出无限的情绪、节奏感和戏剧张力。”<ref>{{citation |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/janetjackson/albums/album/116269/review/5942564/the_velvet_rope |title=Janet Jackson: The Velvet Rope : Music Reviews : Rolling Stone |work=Rolling Stone |accessdate=2010-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080503081338/http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/janetjackson/albums/album/116269/review/5942564/the_velvet_rope |archivedate=2008-05-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>而《華麗的冒險》也被美国国家黑人同性恋领导论坛高度评价，并被授予第十九届{{tsl|en|GLAAD Media Awards|同性恋反诽谤联盟媒体奖}}最佳音乐专辑奖。<ref name=gladd>{{Citation |url=http://www.glaad.org/media/release_detail.php?id=4308 |title=Janet Jackson to be Honored at 19th Annual GLAAD Media Awards in Los Angeles |accessdate=2008-06-10 |last=McCarthy |first=Marc |publisher=[[Gay_&_Lesbian_Alliance_Against_Defamation|Gay & Lesbian Alliance Against Defamation]] |date=2008-04-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080608152724/http://www.glaad.org/media/release_detail.php?id=4308 |archivedate=2008年6月8日 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

1998年，珍妮展开了自己名为{{tsl|en|The Velvet Rope World Tour|The Velvet Rope World Tour}}的世界巡演，总共跨越了欧洲，北美，非洲，亚洲和大洋洲等地区。《洛杉矶时报》的Robert Hilburn报道到：“这次巡演犹如一出充满了魅力与企图心的百老汇歌舞剧，而唯一的目的就是为了凸显出她是这场演出的‘创作者和导演’。“<ref name="broadway">{{Citation |last=Hilburn |first=Robert | title=Janet Jackson Learns The Ropes\ Singer Learns To Like Herself On The Way To Creating The Lavishly Staged Velvet Rope Tour | newspaper=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette| page=G3| date=1998-09-20|issn=1068-624X}}</ref>而由HBO电视台制作的演唱会特辑《The Velvet Rope: Live in Madison Square Garden》更是吸引了全美1500万的电视观众，将其他四大主要电视网的同时段收视率远远的甩在了身后。<ref>{{Citation | title = HBO's Exclusive Live Concert Event Janet: The Velvet Rope | publisher = [[Time_Warner|Time Warner]] | date = 1998-10-14 | url = http://www.timewarner.com/corp/newsroom/pr/0,20812,666900,00.html | accessdate = 2008-03-09 | archive-date = 2007-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070927011205/http://www.timewarner.com/corp/newsroom/pr/0,20812,666900,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>这场演唱会特辑也使HBO电视台入围了四项[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]并最终获得一项大奖。<ref>{{Citation |url=http://books.google.com/?id=Fz0DAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA57&dq=%22janet+jackson%22+%22nominations%22&cd=3#v=onepage&q=%22janet%20jackson%22%20%22nominations%22 |title=Jet - Google Books |publisher= |accessdate=2010-06-29 |date=1999-08-16}}</ref>珍妮也向[[克林·鲍威尔|克林·鲍威尔]]发起成立的非盈利组织{{tsl|en|America's Promise|美国希望联盟}}捐出了一部分门票，以帮助儿童和青年健康成长。<ref>{{citation|author=Kim McAvoy|title=HBO makes the most of music|newspaper=Broadcasting & Cable|volume=128|issue=36|page=30}}</ref>

1998年11月，珍妮与丈夫Elizondo Jr.分居。<ref>{{Citation |last1=Ryon |first1=Ruth | title=Hot Property; Westside at End of Her 'Rope'; Home Edition| newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | page=K1 | date=1999-04-18}}</ref>随着她的世界巡演于1999年结束，珍妮开始在其他艺术家的音乐作品中客串，包括在电影《{{tsl|en|How Stella Got Her Groove Back (soundtrack)|当老牛遇到嫩草}}》(How Stella Got Her Groove Back)的原声专辑中，与[[:en:Shaggy_(musician)|Shaggy's]]合作的《{{tsl|en|Luv Me, Luv Me|Luv Me, Luv Me}}》；电影《亲情密西西比》(Down on the Delta)原声专辑中的《God's Stepchild》；与{{tsl|en|Blackstreet|BLACKstreet}}合作的[[:en:Girlfriend/Boyfriend、Girlfriend/Boyfriend|:en:Girlfriend/Boyfriend、Girlfriend/Boyfriend]]；以及与[[:en:Busta_Rhymes|Busta Rhymes]]合作的《{{tsl|en|What's It Gonna Be?!|What's It Gonna Be?!}}》，她也与[[Elton_John|Elton John]]一起推出了歌曲《I Know the Truth》。1999年的[[世界音乐奖|世界音乐奖]]上她也从歌坛传奇[[雪儿|雪儿]]手中接过了一座'''杰出贡献奖'''。<ref name="World Music Awards">{{Citation | title = Global Pulse: Smith, Hill Top World Awards | work = Billboard | date = 1999-05-06 | url = http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=947178 | accessdate = 2008-09-16 | archive-date = 2010-11-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101129195419/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=947178 | dead-url = no }}</ref>1999年末，《公告牌》杂志将她誉为20世纪90年代最成功的女歌手第二名，仅次于[[玛丽亚·凯莉|玛丽亚·凯莉]]<ref>{{Citation | last1 = Mayfield | first1 = Geoff | title = Totally '90s: Diary of a decade | volume = 111 | issue = 112 | newspaper=Billboard | date = 1999-12-25 | issn = 0006-2510}}</ref>

=== 2000–2003：《肥佬教授2：我们才是一家人》和《珍爱》 ===
2000年7月，珍妮主演了自己的第二部电影《{{tsl|en|Nutty Professor II: The Klumps|肥佬教授2：我们才是一家人}}》,在片中她饰演[[埃迪·墨菲|埃迪·墨菲]]的女友Denise Gaines教授。这成为了珍妮第二部票房排行榜冠军电影，上映首周的周末票房成绩就突破4200万美元。<ref>{{Citation | last= LaSalle | first=Mick | title=`Professor' Moves Out Smartly / Hollywood's summer better than expected| newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle | page=D1 | date= 2000-07-31}}</ref><ref>{{Citation | title=Box Office; Home Edition| newspaper=Los Angeles Times | page=F–28 | date= 2000-08-03}}</ref>而在电影的原声大碟中，她演唱的歌曲《[[Doesn't_Really_Matter|Doesn't Really Matter]]》也成为了她第九支公告牌单曲榜冠军单曲。同年，珍妮的丈夫提请离婚。《娱乐周刊》的Jeff Gordinier报道到：十三年前杰克逊与Elizondo相识，8年后“（两人）结婚，但是约定不仅向公众隐瞒，甚至连珍妮的父亲都毫不知情。”<ref name="Gordinier">{{Citation | last=Gordinier | first=Jeff | title=Will the real Janet Jackson please stand up? Is the seductive superstar an enigma wrapped in a riddle? Or just your average nasty girl with a taste for pleasure and pain?| newspaper=Entertainment Weekly | page=36 | date= 2001-05-04}}</ref>Elizondo提出了一项高达数百万美元的离婚诉讼，要求分割珍妮至少1000万至2500万美元的财产，这场官司直到2003年才落下帷幕。<ref name="Gordinier"/><ref>{{Citation | last= McElroy | first=Quindelda | title=Ex-hubbies can cash in| newspaper=[[The_Atlanta_Journal-Constitution|The Atlanta Journal-Constitution]] | page=E.2 | date= 2007-04-21}}</ref>

2001年5月，珍妮因“细腻而精致的音乐，广受各界好评的声誉，对社会问题的关注以及创纪录的唱片销量”而被授予了[[美国音乐奖|美国音乐奖]]'''{{tsl|en|American Music Award of Merit|特殊贡献奖}}'''。<ref>{{Citation | title = Billboard Bits: AMAs, They Might Be Giants, Ricky Scaggs | work = Billboard | date = 2001-01-04 | url = http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=411513 | accessdate = 2008-05-03 | archive-date = 2012-11-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121102140506/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=411513 | dead-url = no }}</ref>与此同时，她也因对音乐、音乐录影带和流行文化的巨大贡献，以及对MTV时代人群的巨大影响力，而被授予第一届'''{{tsl|en|MTV Icon|MTV 辉煌巨星}}奖'''。<ref name="mtvICON">{{Citation | last = Jeckell | first = Barry | title = MTV To Honor Janet Jackson | work = Billboard | date = 2001-01-10 | url = http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=415363 | accessdate = 2008-03-16 | archive-date = 2010-11-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101129194309/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=415363 | dead-url = no }}</ref>珍妮的第七张专辑《[[珍愛_(珍娜·傑克森專輯)|珍愛]]》与2001年4月上市发行，上榜首周即排行专辑榜第一。<ref name="Billboard Album peaks"/>而首周65万张的专辑销量，也是她职业生涯中的新纪录。<ref>{{Citation | last = Martens | first = Todd | title = Janet Reigns Supreme On Billboard Charts | work = Billboard | date = 2001-05-03 | url = http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=857415 | accessdate = 2008-04-17 | archive-date = 2012-11-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121102140523/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=857415 | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]的资深编辑{{tsl|en|Stephen Thomas Erlewine|Stephen Thomas Erlewine}}形容这张专辑“是一次超过70分钟的，奢华、感性以及舒适的音乐旅程，甚至比你更懂得你自己的需求。”《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的首席娱乐记者{{tsl|en|Jon Pareles|Jon Pareles}}评论道：将节奏布鲁斯与嘻哈音乐完美契合，杰克逊女士创造了一个令人目不暇接的奢华新体验。<ref>{{Citation| last = Erlewine | first = Stephen Thomas | title = All for You > Review |publisher=Allmusic | year = 2001 | url = {{Allmusic|class=album|id=r564427|pure_url=yes}} | accessdate = 2008-07-20}}</ref><ref>{{Citation| last = Pareles | first = Jon | title = Album of the Week |work=The New York Times | date = 2001-05-04 | url = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C0DE7D91238F937A35756C0A9679C8B63 | accessdate = 2008-07-20}}</ref>

专辑的标题主打曲《[[All_for_You_(珍娜·傑克森單曲)|All for You]]》首周仅靠电台点播率即杀入单曲榜，排名十四。<ref name="Radio Record">{{Citation | last = vanHorn | first = Teri | title = Janet Jackson Single Breaks Radio, Chart Records | publisher = MTV | date = 2001-03-09 | url = http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1441454/20010309/jackson_janet.jhtml | accessdate = 2008-05-23 | archive-date = 2009-07-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090724155428/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1441454/20010309/jackson_janet.jhtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>MTV的Teri VanHorn形容珍妮因这首打破电台播放记录的歌曲而成为“'''广播皇后'''”。<ref name="Radio Record"/>单曲正式发售之后毫无悬念的摘得了单曲榜的冠军，并连续七周排名第一。<ref>{{Citation | last = Martens | first = Todd | title = Seven And Counting For Janet At No. 1 | work = Billboard | date = 2001-05-17 | url = http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=869127 | accessdate = 2008-04-17 | archive-date = 2012-11-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121102140540/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=869127 | dead-url = no }}</ref>它也同时获得了2001年[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]最佳舞曲唱片奖。<ref name="Grammy Awards"/>专辑中的第二波主打曲《[[:en:Someone_to_Call_My_Lover|Someone to Call My Lover]]》巧妙的选用了{{tsl|en|America (band)|America's}}乐队的名曲《{{tsl|en|Ventura Highway|Ventura Highway}}》中经典的吉他旋律，在单曲榜上最高排名第三。<ref>{{Citation | last = Caulfield | first = Keith | title = Ask Billboard | work = Billboard | date = 2006-12-24 | url = http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003524980 | accessdate = 2008-04-17 | archive-date = 2012-10-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020073734/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003524980 | dead-url = no }}</ref>《All for You》由RIAA认证为双白金专辑，全球累计销量超过900万张。<ref name="cert"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chartsinfrance.net/Janet-Jackson/news-68976.html |title=Janet Jackson dévoile la vidéo de "Make Me" |work=Charts in France |accessdate=2010-09-28 |archive-date=2013-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509222818/http://www.chartsinfrance.net/Janet-Jackson/news-68976.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

珍妮·杰克逊的巡演{{tsl|en|All for You Tour|All for You Tour}}与2001年7月展开，《洛杉矶时报》的流行音乐评论员Robert Hilburn却给演唱会一个负面的评价，认为[[瑪丹娜|瑪丹娜]]的{{tsl|en|Drowned World Tour|Drowned World Tour}}和[[布兰妮·斯皮尔斯|小甜甜布蘭妮]]的[[:en:Dream_Within_a_Dream_Tour|Dream Within a Dream Tour]]更加的出色，他说：“杰克逊已经35岁了，只比[[瑪丹娜|瑪丹娜]]年轻8岁，但是她在舞台上的表现却更加像正处青少年的[[布兰妮·斯皮尔斯|小甜甜布蘭妮]]。[[瑪丹娜|瑪丹娜]]懂得去挖掘我们内心潜在的东西，而杰克逊却只留与表面。”<ref>{{citation|author=Robert Hilburn|title=Jackson's 'All for You' Concert Misses the Beat; The singer's tightly scripted and precisely executed but seemingly adolescent show at Arrowhead Pond pales in comparison with Madonna's recent tour|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=2001-10-01|page=F.1}}</ref>当然，Hilburn的评论也遭到了许多其他乐评家的反驳，他们认为珍妮的演出是出色的。David Massey评论道：“珍妮超越了物质女孩一大截...仅凭一些图片就能认为珍妮的演唱会像布兰妮的？Hello，他们完全不搭界的好哇？”<ref name="All for You Tour">{{Citation | last1= Esparza | first1=Rafael | last2= Massey | first2=David| last3= Scalese| first3=Rudy| title=Let Jackson's Energetic Beat Go On| newspaper=The Los Angeles Times | page=F–4 | date= 2001-10-06}}</ref>Rudy Scalese也认为“珍妮完全没有丢掉自己的节拍，她仍然是我们的'''流行女皇'''！”<ref name="All for You Tour"/>珍妮向{{tsl|en|Boys & Girls Clubs of America|美国男孩女孩俱乐部}}捐献了部门的门票，该基金会的主席Roxanne Spillett非常感谢珍妮对他们事业的支持并说：“她的慷慨资助使得我们能够为年轻人找寻更多的希望和机会。”<ref>{{Citation | title=Janet Jackson Announces 'All for You Tour 2001'; Alliance to Support Boys & Girls Clubs of America; Ticket Proceeds To Be Donated As Part Of Nationwide Campaign| publisher=Business Wire | date= 2001-05-30}}</ref>

2002年，珍妮·杰克逊与[[雷鬼音乐|雷鬼]]乐手{{tsl|en|Beenie Man|Beenie Man}}合作了单曲《{{tsl|en|Feel It Boy|Feel It Boy}}》。但在发现{{tsl|en|Beenie Man|Beenie Man}}之前的音乐作品中经常出现反同言论之后，她对他们的合作感到非常的后悔。随后，她在《[[:en:The_Voice_(newspaper)|The Voice]]》杂志上向她的同性恋歌迷公开道歉。<ref>{{Citation | last = Weekes | first = Danielle | title = I'm Sorry, Says Ms Jackson | work = [[The_Voice_(newspaper)|The Voice]] | date = 2004-10-16 | url = http://www.voice-online.co.uk/content.php?show=5270 | accessdate = 2008-04-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090706020200/http://www.voice-online.co.uk/content.php?show=5270 | archivedate = 2009-07-06 }}</ref>同年，珍妮与唱片制作人[[杰梅因·杜普里|杰梅因·杜普里]]开始约会。

=== 2004–2005：超级盃露乳事件和《达米塔·乔》 ===
<!-- 注释: [[Image:Janet_Jackson_&_Justin_Timberlake's_wardrobe_malfunction.jpg|thumb]] -->
2004年2月，珍妮受邀在[[超级盃|超级盃]]半场休息时[[第三十八届超級碗中場表演爭議|表演]]，当演唱完自己的两首歌曲《All for You》和《Rhythm Nation》后，她与歌手[[贾斯汀·提姆布莱克|贾斯汀·提姆布莱克]]一同表演了后者的歌曲《{{tsl|en|Rock Your Body|Rock Your Body}}》。当贾斯汀唱完歌中的歌词“最后让你脱光光(gonna have you naked by the end of this song)”后，他扯掉了珍妮的上衣，使其右乳通过卫星转播在将近9000万观众面前完全暴露（虽然[[乳頭|乳頭]]有被一个金黃色圓狀的[[乳貼|乳貼]]遮住而沒有暴露）了0.8秒。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2009/01/18/historical-super-bowl-tv-ratings/11044 |title=TVbythenumbers.com |accessdate=2012-01-22 |archive-date=2010-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100208213536/http://tvbythenumbers.com/2009/01/18/historical-super-bowl-tv-ratings/11044 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>表演结束后珍妮立即向大众道歉，并声称这只是一次事故而非刻意安排，原先预想的舞台效果只是贾斯汀撕掉外侧的皮质紧身衣，而留红色的胸罩在身上。<ref name="apologeticjackson">{{Citation | title = Apologetic Jackson says 'costume reveal' went awry | publisher = CNN | date = 2004-02-03 | url = http://www.cnn.com/2004/US/02/02/superbowl.jackson/ | accessdate = 2006-05-20 | archive-date = 2010-02-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100218110403/http://www.cnn.com/2004/US/02/02/superbowl.jackson/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>她还表示：“如果有冒犯到任何人，我真心的表示歉意。但这真的不是我的本意...MTV、CBS以及[[国家橄榄球联盟|国家橄榄球联盟]]都不曾预计到会发生什么，但是不幸的是，最后还是出现了差错。”<ref>{{Citation | title = Jackson's apology can't stem mass anger | publisher = [[ESPN|ESPN]] | url = http://sports.espn.go.com/nfl/playoffs03/news/story?id=1724968&partnersite=espn | accessdate = 2008-03-09 | archive-date = 2008-06-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080610061754/http://sports.espn.go.com/nfl/playoffs03/news/story?id=1724968&partnersite=espn | dead-url = no }}</ref>贾斯汀也表达了自己的歉意，并表示这只是一起普通的[[走光_(行为)|走光]]事件。<ref name="apologeticjackson"/>《[[时代周刊|时代周刊]]》报道说，这0.8秒是数位录影机[[TiVo|TiVo]]上被重播次数最多的画面，而《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志的Monte Burke更宣称，这一事件也让TiVo公司的签约订购额大增。<ref>{{Citation | title=Numbers | newspaper=Time |volume=163 |issue=7 | page=19 | date=2004-02-16|issn=0040-781X}}</ref><ref>{{Citation |last=Burke |first=Monte |title=The Ripple Effect |newspaper=Time |volume=173 |issue=4 |page=46 |date=2004-03-01 |issn=0015-6914 |url=http://www.forbes.com/forbes/2004/0301/046a.html |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120629002505/http://www.forbes.com/forbes/2004/0301/046a.html |archivedate=2012-06-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>2007年版的《[[吉尼斯世界纪录大全|吉尼斯世界纪录大全]]》中称这一事件是互联网史上被搜索最多的以及被搜索最多的新闻事件。<ref>{{Citation | title = Star-studded 2007 edition of Guinness World Records released | publisher = [[CBC_News|CBC News]] | date = 2006-09-29 | url = http://www.cbc.ca/arts/story/2006/09/29/guinness-record-book.html | accessdate = 2006-09-30 | archive-date = 2007-02-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070219075828/http://www.cbc.ca/arts/story/2006/09/29/guinness-record-book.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>虽然[[CBS|CBS]]、[[国家橄榄球联盟|国家橄榄球联盟]]以及MTV电视台（CBS电视台的姊妹台，并负责半场休息表演）均表示对事件事先并不知情，且不愿对其负责。但是美国联邦通信委会最后仍以疏于管理的名义向CBS开出了一张55万美元的巨额罚单。<ref>{{Citation |last=Davidson |first=Paul | title=FCC loses appeal of 'wardrobe malfunction' fine | newspaper=USA Today | page=2b| date=2008-07-22|issn=0734-7456}}</ref>

事件之后CBS高层极为震怒，扬言如果珍妮和贾斯汀不公开向电视网道歉，将立即封杀两人并且他们也将不被获邀参加一周之后即将举办的第四十六届[[葛莱美奖|葛莱美奖]]颁奖典礼。贾斯汀·提姆布莱克最终妥协，向CBS公开道歉。但是珍妮坚持这只是一次很普通的走光事件而拒绝向CBS道歉。<ref>{{Citation | last = Leopold | first = Todd | title = Beyonce tops with five Grammys | publisher = CNN | date = 2004-02-09 | url = http://www.cnn.com/2004/SHOWBIZ/Music/02/08/grammy.night/index.html | accessdate = 2008-04-03 | archive-date = 2008-07-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080727023813/http://www.cnn.com/2004/SHOWBIZ/Music/02/08/grammy.night/index.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>而珍妮的男友Jermaine Dupri也从葛莱美奖组委会中请辞，以表达对自己女友的支持。<ref>{{Citation | last = Gallo | first = Phil | title = Beyonce beats the rap at the Grammys | work = Variety | date = 2004-02-09 | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117899800.html?categoryid=16&cs=1 | accessdate = 2008-04-03 | archive-date = 2008-10-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081011213443/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117899800.html?categoryid=16&cs=1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>这一事件也终止了珍妮为ABC电视台主演传奇女歌手、民权主义斗士[[莲纳·荷恩|莲纳·荷恩]]的电视传记影片的计划。据报道称，莲纳·荷恩为露乳事件大为光火，并极力要求ABC电视台另谋其他演员来饰演自己。因为珍妮的此前的行为，让莲纳觉得就算自己退出也愿意。<ref>{{Citation | title = Horne: Janet Jackson, don't play me | agency = Associated Press | publisher = CNN | date = 2004-02-04 | url = http://www.cnn.com/2004/SHOWBIZ/TV/02/24/tv.janetjackson.ap/ | accessdate = 2008-04-03 | format = – <sup>[http://scholar.google.co.uk/scholar?hl=en&lr=&q=intitle%3AHorne%3A+Janet+Jackson%2C+don%27t+play+me&as_publication=&as_ylo=&as_yhi=&btnG=Search Scholar search]</sup> | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050220135401/http://www.cnn.com/2004/SHOWBIZ/TV/02/24/tv.janetjackson.ap/ | archivedate = 2005年2月20日 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>

2004年5月，珍妮的第八张录音室专辑《{{tsl|en|Damita Jo (album)|Damita Jo}}》上市发行，这张专辑的名称来自于歌手的中间名。专辑首周上榜排名第二。<ref name="Billboard Album peaks"/><ref name="DA SCOOP ON 'DAMITA JO'">{{Citation | title = No. 1 Usher Holds Janet To No. 2 Debut | work = Billboard | url = http://www.billboard.com/#/news/no-1-usher-holds-janet-to-no-2-debut-1000481059.story | accessdate = 2009-10-21 | archive-date = 2012-07-28 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20120728/http://www.billboard.com/%23/artist/eddie-murphy/chart-history/1173?f=305&g=Albums#/news/no-1-usher-holds-janet-to-no-2-debut-1000481059.story | dead-url = no }}</ref>Allmusic的{{tsl|en|Stephen Thomas Erlewine|Stephen Thomas Erlewine}}描述这张专辑：“就像听觉上的硬核色情杂志一样，毫无想象力且充满了简单的重复。”<ref name="STE">{{Citation |last=Erlewine |first=Stephen Thomas | title = ''Damita Jo'' |publisher=Allmusic | year = 2004| url = {{Allmusic|class=album|id=r680820|pure_url=yes}} | accessdate = 2009-02-08}}</ref>但《[[:en:Blender_(magazine)|Blender]]》杂志的{{tsl|en|Ann Powers|Ann Powers}}则认为这张专辑：“结构巧妙，条理清晰。足以扭转人们因露乳事件而对珍妮产生的负面看法。”<ref>{{Citation |last=Powers |first=Ann |title=Janet Jackson: Damita Jo Review on Blender |work=[[Blender_(magazine)|Blender]] |date=2004-03-03 |url=http://www.blender.com/guide/reviews.aspx?id=2049 |accessdate=2009-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050214124547/http://www.blender.com/guide/reviews.aspx?id=2049 |archive-date=2005-02-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>RIAA最终将《Damita Jo》认证为白金唱片，而在世界范围内也销售近300万张。<ref name="cert"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.people.com/people/janet_jackson/biography/0,,20004356_10,00.html |title=Janet Jackson Biography : People.com |publisher=[[People_(magazine)|People]] |accessdate=2010-08-16 |archive-date=2011-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110307093553/http://www.people.com/people/janet_jackson/biography/0%2C%2C20004356_10%2C00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>虽然专辑在专辑榜上成绩不错，最高排名第二，但是专辑中的单曲却没有一首能超越Top40的名次。《公告牌》杂志的Keith Caulfield说：“对像珍妮·杰克逊这样一位拥有27支Top10单曲，其中10支更是冠军单曲的歌手来说，这样的成绩应该算是令人失望的。”<ref name="DA SCOOP ON 'DAMITA JO'"/>《公告牌》杂志的Clover Hope评论道：“专辑惨败的一个重大原因就是超级盃事件对人们的影响”。而珍妮时任维京唱片黑人音乐部门总裁的男友Jermaine Dupri也宣称：“感受不到母公司一丁点的支持。”<ref name="Together Again">{{Citation | last = Hope | first = Clover | title = Together Again: Janet Jackson | work = Billboard | date = 2008-02-04 | url = http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003706565 | accessdate = 2008-03-23 | archive-date = 2012-12-08 | archive-url = https://archive.today/20121208131238/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003706565%23/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003706565 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2004年4月10日，珍妮主持了一集《[[周末夜现场|周末夜现场]]》(Saturday Night Live)并演唱了两首自己的歌曲，同年她还在美国情景喜剧《[[威尔与格蕾丝|威尔与格蕾丝]]》(Will & Grace)中客串演出，饰演自己。<ref>{{Citation |last1=Hay |first1=Carla | title=The Billboard Backbeat | newspaper=Billboard |volume=116 |issue=35 | pages=60–61 | date=2004-08-28}}</ref>2004年11月，她因艺术上的巨大成功而入选了美国百大黑人。<ref>{{Citation | title=New York Chapter Of 100 Black Men Honors Janet Jackson, Hank Aaron, Johnnetta Cole, Willie Gary | newspaper=Jet |volume=106 |issue=23 | page=28 | date=2004-12-06|issn=0021-5996}}</ref>虽然《{{tsl|en|New York Amsterdam News|New York Amsterdam News}}》报道称：部分评委会的委员因超级盃事件对这位38岁的歌手持保留意见，但是组委会的主席Paul Williams却解释道：“瑕不掩瑜，一次无心之错并不能代表这位歌手的全部。”<ref>{{Citation |last1=Browne |first1= J. Zamgba | title=Janet Jackson stirs up controversy at annual gala of 100 Black Men | newspaper=[[New_York_Amsterdam_News|New York Amsterdam News]] |volume=95 |issue=47 | page=8 | date=2004-11-18|issn=0028-7121}}</ref><ref>{{Citation |last1= Berry |first1= Steve | title=Janet Jackson stirs up controversy at annual gala of 100 Black Men | newspaper=[[The_Columbus_Dispatch|The Columbus Dispatch]] |volume=95 |issue=47 | page=12.D| date=2004-11-11|issn=1074-097X}}</ref>2005年6月，珍妮也被[[:en:Human_Rights_Campaign|Human Rights Campaign]]这一同性恋权益组织授予了一项人道主义奖。{{tsl|en|AIDS Project Los Angeles|洛杉矶艾滋病研究防疫中心}}也为这位歌手多年来利用自己的知名度为组织筹款而表达感谢。

=== 2006–2007：《珍情告白》和《我为什么结婚了？》 ===
[[File:Janet_Jackson.jpg|thumb]]
为了推广自己的第九张录音室专辑《{{link-en|20 Y.O.|20 Y.O.}}》，珍妮登上了《{{tsl|en|US Weekly|US Weekly}}》杂志2006年6月号的封面，这也使这期杂志创下了创刊以来的发行纪录。<ref>the best-selling issue in Us Weekly history was the Janet Jackson mag, which sold a record 1.4 million the week of May 26. {{Citation|last=Kelly |first=Keith| title = MLad Mag's Coverup – Fhm Wraps Racy Glossy After Hudson News Complaint| newspaper=New York Post | date=2006-06-23 | page = 36}}</ref>维京唱片与该年9月正式发行了这张专辑，专辑在[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|告示牌專輯榜]]上最高排名第二。<ref name="Billboard Album peaks"/>《公告牌》杂志的Janine Coveney说：专辑的标题“20年来”，是为了纪念珍妮在1986年发行的那张标志性与突破性兼具的创纪录专辑《Control》。“<ref name="Janet's Juggernaut">{{Citation |url = http://www.billboard.com/#/news/janet-s-juggernaut-1003087367.story |title = Janet's Juggernaut |last = Coveney |first = Janine |newspaper = Billboard |date = 2006-09-05 |accessdate = 2010-09-13 |archive-date = 2012-07-28 |archive-url = https://archive.is/20120728/http://www.billboard.com/%23/artist/eddie-murphy/chart-history/1173?f=305&g=Albums#/news/janet-s-juggernaut-1003087367.story |dead-url = no }}</ref>而《滚石》杂志的Evan Serpick说：”这张珍妮·杰克逊新专辑的标题，指代的是她20年前那张伟大的，并以其中的歌曲《Nasty》和《What Have You Done for Me Lately》引领一代风格的专辑《Control》。但如果我们是她，我们绝对不会去做比较。“<ref>{{Citation |last=Serpick |first=Evan |title=Janet Jackson: 20 Y.O. : Music Reviews : Rolling Stone |date=2006-10-03 |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/janetjackson/albums/album/11571388/review/11942285/20_yo |accessdate=2010-07-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080503060722/http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/janetjackson/albums/album/11571388/review/11942285/20_yo |archivedate=2008-05-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>而《Newsday》的Glenn Gamboa却给了专辑一个正面的评价，她在文中指出：”在《20 Y.O.》中，歌手舍弃了所有所谓突破自由极限或表述自己观点的条条框框，保持了今年来她专辑的最大尺度和性感张力。这张专辑中体现的只有舞蹈和她的R&B本质。<ref>{{Citation | last = Gamboa | first = Glenn | title = How Janet got her groove back | work = Newsday | year = 2006 | url = http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/ny-janet0926,0,1192261.story?coll=ny-entertainment-headlines | accessdate = 2008-07-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071013222222/http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/ny-janet0926,0,1192261.story?coll=ny-entertainment-headlines | archivedate = 2007年10月13日 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>

专辑的主打单曲《{{tsl|en|Call on Me (Janet Jackson song)|Call on Me}}》由珍妮与著名饶舌歌手[[耐利|奈利]]合作，最高排名单曲榜第25位。<ref name="singles peaks"/> 《20 Y.O.》由RIAA认证为白金唱片，在美国销售了逾67万9000张，并在全球销售了近120万张。<ref name="cert"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003695730#/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003695730 |title=Ask Billboard |work=Billboard |accessdate=2010-07-14 |archive-date=2012-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107170936/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003695730#/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003695730 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Citation |url=http://books.google.com/?id=PNMDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA74&dq=Janet+Jackson,+Discipline,+worldwide+million&cd=1#v=onepage&q=Janet%20Jackson%2C%20Discipline%2C%20worldwide%20million&f=false |title=Ebony - Apr 2008 |publisher=|accessdate=2010-06-05 |date=2008-04}}</ref>《公告牌》报道说：“随着《20 Y.O.》的发行，令珍妮完成了与维京公司的唱片合约。而珍妮的男友，也是《20 Y.O.》的专辑制作人，负责维京黑人音乐事业部的Jermaine Dupri也因专辑的”糟糕表现”而离开了公司。<ref>{{Citation |last1=Mitchell |first1=Gail |last2=Garrity |first2=Brian| title=Dupri Exit Fuels Rumors | newspaper=Billboard |volume=118 |issue=44 | page=10 | date=2006-11-04|issn=0006-2510}}</ref>

2007年1月，珍妮被《福布斯》杂志评选为世界上最富有的女艺人第七名，估计她的资产总额超过1亿5000万美元。<ref>{{Citation | last = Goldman | first = Lea | coauthors = Kiri Blakeley | title = The 20 Richest Women In Entertainment | work = Forbes | date = 2007-01-18 | url = http://www.forbes.com/2007/01/17/richest-women-entertainment-tech-media-cz_lg_richwomen07_0118womenstars_lander.html | accessdate = 2008-09-03 | archive-date = 2007-10-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071006084807/http://www.forbes.com/2007/01/17/richest-women-entertainment-tech-media-cz_lg_richwomen07_0118womenstars_lander.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>同年，她在Tyler Perry的新片《{{tsl|en|Why Did I Get Married?|我为什么结婚了？}}》(Why Did I Get Married)中饰演了一名名为Patrica的心理医生。该片凭借首周2140万的票房成绩，成为珍妮第三部北美票房冠军电影。<ref>{{Citation| last = Ryan | first = Joal | title = Just Call It Tyler Perry's Box Office |work=[[E!_News|E! News]] | date = 2007-10-15| url = http://uk.eonline.com/uberblog/b56440_Just_Call_It_Tyler_Perrys_Box_Office.html | accessdate = 2010-09-17 }}</ref>《[[综艺|综艺]]》杂志的Ronnie Scheib形容珍妮在剧中的表现迷人且富含魅力。而《波士顿环球报》的记者Wesley Morris则评价珍妮给这个角色带来了一种“温柔的权力”。<ref>{{Citation| last = Scheib| first = Ronnie | title = Tyler Perry's Why Did I Get Married? | newspaper=Variety | date = October 2007| page=32|volume=408|issue=10|issn=0042-2738}}</ref><ref>{{Citation | last = Morris | first = Wesley | title = 'Married' is involving, if not blissful | work = The Boston Globe | date = 2007-10-13 | url = http://www.boston.com/movies/display?display=movie&id=10489 | accessdate = 2008-07-29 | archive-date = 2008-12-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081223014618/http://www.boston.com/movies/display?display=movie&id=10489 | dead-url = no }}</ref>珍妮也凭借这一角色在2008年2月获得了美国[[有色人种促进协会形象奖|有色人种促进协会形象奖]]最佳女配角奖。<ref>{{Citation |last1= Christian |first1=Margena A | title=NAACP Honors Showbiz Veterans, Newcomers At Image Awards | newspaper=[[Jet_(magazine)|Jet]] |volume=113 |issue=8 | page=52 | date=2008-03-03}}</ref>

=== 2008–2009： 《惩罚》，迈克尔·杰克逊之死，以及《冠军纪录》 ===
[[File:Janet_Jackson_17.jpg|thumb]]
2007年，珍妮·杰克逊与环球旗下的[[:en:Island_Records|Island Records]]签约，并2008年2月发行了自己第十张录音室专辑《{{tsl|en|Discipline (Janet Jackson album)|Discipline}}》。专辑再一次登上了美国专辑榜的第一名。<ref name="Billboard Album peaks"/>《娱乐周刊》的Margeaux Watson说：“她那些为了男孩子痴迷的俗气歌词听起来就像歌手害了相思病一样，肯定又会将这位过气的流行偶像推向评论家笔下的风口浪尖。”<ref>{{Citation | last = Watson | first = Margeaux | title = Discipline Music Review | newspaper = Entertainment Weekly | year = 2008 | url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20178215,00.html | accessdate = 2008-06-14 | archive-date = 2008-05-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080528181123/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20178215,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>《Allmusic》的Andy Kellman却认为：“虽然珍妮已经不可能再像在80年代末那样的呼风唤雨，但是就此将她忘却也是不现实的。”<ref>{{citation|last=Kellman|first=Andy|title=Discipline|url={{Allmusic|class=album|id=r1313319|pure_url=yes}}|publisher=Allmusic|year=2008|accessdate=2009-10-09}}</ref>她的单曲《{{tsl|en|Feedback (song)|Feedback}}》在单曲榜上最高排名19。<ref name="singles peaks"/>2008年4月，珍妮·杰克逊获得了美国[[同性恋反诽谤同盟|同性恋反诽谤同盟]]{{tsl|en|GLAAD Media Awards|先锋奖}}(GLAAD Media Awards Vanguard Award)，以表彰她多年来为同性恋权益所作出的巨大贡献。<ref name=gladd/>美国同性恋反诽谤同盟的主席Neil G. Giuliano在致辞中说到：“杰克逊女士
一直为同性恋族群作出巨大的贡献，她也一直与我们一道与这个世界上许许多多针对同性恋的歧视与诽谤的现象做着斗争。"<ref name=gladd/>珍妮的第五次大型世界巡回演唱会《{{tsl|en|Rock Witchu Tour|Rock Witchu Tour}}》也在同年9月展开。<ref>{{Citation | last = Harrington | first = Jim | title = Review: The hits kept coming at Janet Jackson's Oakland show | newspaper=[[The_Oakland_Tribune|The Oakland Tribune]] | date = 2008-09-14| issn = 1068-5936}}</ref>但与此同时，她与她的唱片公司的矛盾却日益恶化，专辑的制作人{{tsl|en|Rodney Jerkins|Rodney 'Darkchild' Jerkins}}宣称：”公司并没有好好的负责推广这张专辑，珍妮也没有受到像她这样一位艺术家应该享受到的待遇。“<ref>{{citation|title=Janet Jackson splits with record label|url=http://www.nme.com/news/janet-jackson/39889|newspaper=[[NME|NME]]|date=2008-09-20|accessdate=2009-10-08|archive-date=2009-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090901190252/http://www.nme.com/news/janet-jackson/39889|dead-url=no}}</ref>在与Island Records签约14个月之后，珍妮的新专辑在美国只销售了44万9000张，并没有获得任何的销量认证。《公告牌》报道说，珍妮对唱片公司对她专辑的宣传力度非常不满，”而唱片公司最终也应歌手的要求而与之解约。“<ref name="Concepcion">{{Citation |first=Mariel |last=Concepcion |url=http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/news/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003853412 |title=Janet Jackson Parts Ways With Island Def Jam |work=Billboard |accessdate=2008-09-22 |archive-date=2008-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080923063408/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/news/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003853412 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://new.music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart_watch/51507/week-ending-april-11-2010-bieber-bounces-back/ |title=Week Ending April 11, 2010: Bieber Bounces Back |publisher=Yahoo.com |date=2010-04-14 |accessdate=2010-05-16 |archive-date=2010-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100417002609/http://new.music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart_watch/51507/week-ending-april-11-2010-bieber-bounces-back/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2009年6月，珍妮的兄长，一代传奇巨星迈克尔·杰克逊去世，享年50岁。在2009年的[[黑人娱乐电视大奖|黑人娱乐电视大奖]]上，珍妮代表她的家族，向所有关心他们的人表示感谢，并表达了他们对迈克尔深深的思念：”对于大家而言，迈克尔·杰克逊是一个娱乐符号，是一个象征。对我来说，迈克尔是一个亲人，他将永远活在我们所有人的心中！我代表我和我的家人，向你们每一个人表示感谢，谢谢你们的爱，谢谢你们所有人的支持。我是如此的想念他！”<ref>{{citation|last=Carter|first=Kelley|title=An emotional Janet Jackson thanks fans at BET Awards|newspaper=USA Today|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2009-06-29-bet-awards-jackson_N.htm?csp=34|date=2009-06-28|accessdate=2009-06-28|archive-date=2009-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090702032320/http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2009-06-29-bet-awards-jackson_N.htm?csp=34|dead-url=no}}</ref>其后她接受了《[[时尚芭莎|时尚芭莎]]》的专访，在专访中她透露，在得知她兄长的死讯时，她正在亚特兰大拍摄电影《{{tsl|en|Why Did I Get Married Too?|我为什么又结婚了？}}》(Why Did I Get Married Too?)。在参加完一系列公开的以及家庭私人的悼念会之后，她又开始专注于工作。不看电视，不看报纸，避免一切能联想到迈克尔的事物，她说：“虽然面对现实也非常的重要，但是这也不能说是在逃避。只是有时候，你真的需要将自己抽离一小会。”<ref name="HB">{{citation|last=Brown|first=Laura|title=Janet Jackson Takes Control|newspaper=[[Harper's_Bazaar|Harper's Bazaar]]|page=244|date=October 2009|issn=244}}</ref>与此同时，她与相恋7年的男友Jermaine Dupri分手。<ref name="HB"/>2009年9月，她在2009年MTV音乐大奖的颁奖典礼中向迈克尔·杰克逊致敬的表演单元中演唱了当年与迈克尔合作的歌曲《Scream》。<ref>{{citation|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1621392/20090913/madonna.jhtml|title=VMAs Kick Off with Madonna and Janet's Tribute to Michael Jackson|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|date=2009-09-13|work=MTV News|accessdate=2009-09-14|archive-date=2009-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090922190441/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1621392/20090913/madonna.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>MTV音乐台的总经理Stephen Friedman说：“没有人能比珍妮更好的抓住表演的精髓并传递一个强烈的讯息。”<ref name="SF">{{citation|last=Kinon|first=Cristina|title=Janet Jackson to do dance tribute for Michael to kick off VMAs|newspaper=Daily News|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv/2009/09/11/2009-09-11_janet_jackson_to_do_dance_tribute_for_michael_to_kick_off_vmas.html|date=2009-09-11|accessdate=2009-09-19|archive-date=2009-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090915003205/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv/2009/09/11/2009-09-11_janet_jackson_to_do_dance_tribute_for_michael_to_kick_off_vmas.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她与数位知名的舞者在表演中合作，而她长期的艺术指导Gil Duldulao则负责策划了整场演出。<ref name="SF"/>这次演出也获得了评论界的高度赞扬，《娱乐周刊》的Michael Slezak评论道：”她在舞台上努力的排练，就像一名初出茅庐力争上游的新晋艺人一般，而这种向迈克尔致敬的感情，是实实在在发自内心的。“<ref>{{citation|last=Slezak|first=Michael|title=Janet Jackson single-handedly saves MTV VMA tribute to Michael Jackson|url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2009/09/14/janet-jackson-michael-jackson-vmas-2009|date=2009-09-13|newspaper=Entertainment Weekly|accessdate=2009-09-16|archive-date=2009-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090925023531/http://music-mix.ew.com/2009/09/14/janet-jackson-michael-jackson-vmas-2009/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在MTV音乐录影带奖颁奖典礼之后，珍妮在自己的官网上公布以[[流媒体|流媒体]]的形式公开了自己的新单曲《{{tsl|en|Make Me|Make Me}}》，其后以数字下载的方式发行。<ref>{{citation|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|title=Janet Jackson Releases New Single Following VMA Performance|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1621430/20090914/jackson_janet.jhtml|publisher=MTV|date=2009-09-14|accessdate=2009-09-14|archive-date=2009-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090922205956/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1621430/20090914/jackson_janet.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>这首单曲也成为珍妮第19支公告牌舞曲榜冠军。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/#/column/chartbeat/chart-highlights-country-dance-club-play-1004054789.story|title=Chart Highlights: Adult Contemporary, Pop, Jazz & More|date=2009-12-21|work=Billboard|accessdate=2009-12-21|archive-date=2012-07-28|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120728/http://www.billboard.com/%23/artist/eddie-murphy/chart-history/1173?f=305&g=Albums#/column/chartbeat/chart-highlights-country-dance-club-play-1004054789.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>在当年的米兰时装周期间，珍妮也主持了美国艾滋病研究基金会的慈善晚会。基金会的CEO Kevin Robert Frost说：”我们为珍妮在米兰所作的一切感到无比自豪...一直以来珍妮都在为世界防艾与抗艾事业做出巨大贡献。“<ref>{{citation|title=Janet Jackson to Chair amfAR's Inaugural Milan Fashion Week Event|publisher=amfAR|url=http://www.amfar.org/spotlight/article.aspx?id=7847&terms=janet+jackson|date=2009-08-24|accessdate=2009-09-28|archive-date=2010-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100306215317/http://www.amfar.org/spotlight/article.aspx?id=7847&terms=janet+jackson|dead-url=no}}</ref>在慈善晚会上，一双原本迈克尔曾想在《[[This_Is_It_(迈克尔·杰克逊演唱会)|This Is It]]》演唱会上穿的镶满水晶的舞靴也以14650美元的高价拍卖出售，当晚总计为基金会筹得了110万美元的善款。珍妮激动的说：”我想向每一位在这里的时尚圈人士表达感谢，感谢你们对美国艾滋病研究基金会和抗治艾滋病事业的支持。“<ref>{{citation|last=Colleen|first=Barry|title=Charity Auction Nets $1.1 Million for AIDS|url=http://ca.music.yahoo.com/read/news/61994603|publisher=[[Yahoo!_Music|Yahoo! Music]]|agency=Associated Press|date=2009-09-29|accessdate=2010-10-17|archive-date=2010-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100825052158/http://ca.music.yahoo.com/read/news/61994603|dead-url=no}}</ref>2009年11月，她的第二张精选专辑《[[:en:Number_Ones_(Janet_Jackson_album)|Number Ones]]》（美国以外的地区专辑名为《The Best》）由[[环球唱片|环球唱片]]和[[EMI|EMI]]共同发行。<ref>{{Citation | title = Janet Jackson's hits CD on its way | publisher = [[United_Press_International|United Press International]] | date = 2008-10-13 | url = http://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/Music/2009/10/13/Janet-Jacksons-hits-CD-on-its-way/UPI-31331255480825/ | accessdate = 2008-10-13 | archive-date = 2009-10-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091014233746/http://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/Music/2009/10/13/Janet-Jacksons-hits-CD-on-its-way/UPI-31331255480825/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>精选集在美国专辑榜上最高排名22位，首周销售了37000张。<ref name="Billboard Album peaks"/><ref>{{cite news|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|title=50 Cent's Self Destruct Is Lowest Chart Debut Of His Career|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1627087/20091125/50_cent.jhtml|publisher=MTV|date=2009-11-25|accessdate=2009-11-25|archive-date=2009-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091128004120/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1627087/20091125/50_cent.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后，她应邀在[[2009年全美音乐奖|2009年全美音乐奖]]颁奖典礼上做开场表演，并在2009年12月出席了伦敦{{tsl|en|95.8 Capital FM|Capital FM}}电台在[[O2体育馆|O2体育馆]]举办的《{{tsl|en|Jingle Bell Ball|Jingle Bell Ball}}》演唱会。作为嘉宾参与演出。<ref>{{citation|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|title=Janet Jackson Kicks Off American Music Awards With Energetic Medley/Singer performed her new single, 'Make Me.'|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1626828/20091122/jackson_janet.jhtml|publisher=MTV|date=2009-11-22|accessdate=2009-11-22|archive-date=2009-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091126125636/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1626828/20091122/jackson_janet.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citation|title=Janet Jackson Capital FM|url=http://www.capitalfm.com/jingle-bell-ball/sunday/artists/janet-jackson/|publisher=[[95.8_Capital_FM|95.8 Capital FM]]|date=2009-10-20|accessdate=2009-10-20|archive-date=2009-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091212094702/http://www.capitalfm.com/jingle-bell-ball/sunday/artists/janet-jackson/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 2010–至今：电影计划、产品代言、《珍我》和《近距离接触》世界巡演 ===
2010年4月，珍妮再一次在Tyler Perry的电影《{{tsl|en|Why Did I Get Married?|我为什么结婚了？}}》(Why Did I Get Married?)的续集《{{tsl|en|Why Did I Get Married Too?|我为什么又结婚了？}}》(Why Did I Get Married Too?)中饰演心理医生Patrica。该剧上映首周即获得了3010万的票房成绩，高居北美周末电影票房排行榜的第二位。<ref>{{citation|last=Flint|first=Joe|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-et-box-officeside5-2010apr05,0,7889804.story|title=Tyler Perry's impressive weekend|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=2010-04-05|accessdate=2010-04-06}}</ref>《波士顿环球报》的Wesley Morris评论该剧是“一场120分钟的情感训练”并认为“看珍妮顶着一头歇斯底里的发型饰演一个歇斯底里的人物重新装修一间乡村俱乐部足足能让你烧掉500大卡的热量。”<ref>{{citation|last=Morris|first=Wesley|title=Tyler Perry’s psychological mayhem cuts deep in ‘Married’ sequel|url=http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/articles/2010/04/03/tyler_perry_cuts_deep_in_married_sequel/|newspaper=The Boston Globe|date=2010-04-03|accessdate=2010-04-06|archive-date=2010-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100406124024/http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/articles/2010/04/03/tyler_perry_cuts_deep_in_married_sequel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《纽约时报》的Mike Hale认为珍妮的表现“充满激情且奇怪的有趣”。《[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]》的Jackie K. Cooper则认为：她是剧中最受瞩目的演员，而为了诠释她的角色，她也不介意大家看到她披头散发的样子。“<ref>{{citation|last=Hale|first=Mike|title=Tyler Perry's Why Did I Get Married Too? (2010): At Couples’ Reunion, Laughs, Then Grief|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/2010/04/03/movies/03tyler.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2010-04-07|accessdate=2010-04-07|archive-date=2010-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100406001041/http://movies.nytimes.com/2010/04/03/movies/03tyler.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citation|last=Cooper|first=Jackie|title="Tyler Perry's Why Did I Get Married Too?": Why Did He Make a Two?|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/jackie-k-cooper/tyler-perrys-why-did-i-ge_b_525126.html|date=2010-04-05|accessdate=2010-04-06|publisher=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|archive-date=2010-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100409152302/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/jackie-k-cooper/tyler-perrys-why-did-i-ge_b_525126.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>珍妮的表演为她赢得了一项[[有色人种促进协会形象奖|有色人种促进协会形象奖]]最佳女主角的提名。<ref>{{citation|title=The 42nd NAACP Image Awards - Motion Picture|url=http://www.naacpimageawards.net/42/nominees-and-honorees/motion-picture/|publisher=[[NAACP_Image_Awards|NAACP Image Awards]]|date=2011-01-12|accessdate=2011-01-12|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110112080712/http://www.naacpimageawards.net/42/nominees-and-honorees/motion-picture/|archivedate=2011-01-12}}</ref>她为专辑将配唱的主题曲《{{tsl|en|Nothing (Janet Jackson song)|Nothing}}》也早于电影上映前发行。<ref>{{citation|last=Rodriguez|first=Jayson|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1632205/20100218/dupri_jermaine.jhtml|title=Jermaine Dupri Says New Janet Jackson Song Is 'A Good Record'|publisher=MTV|date=2010-02-18|accessdate=2010-04-07|archive-date=2010-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100222220143/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1632205/20100218/dupri_jermaine.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年5月，她作为表演嘉宾出席了[[美国偶像_(第九季)|美国偶像 (第九季)]]的决赛现场，表演了自己的名曲《Again》、《Nothing》以及《Nasty》。<ref>{{cite web|last=Downey|first=Ryan J.|date=May 27, 2010|title='American Idol' Finale Ratings the Lowest Since Season One|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1640212/20100527/story.jhtml|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=May 27, 2010|archive-date=2010-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100531174121/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1640212/20100527/story.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2010年，作为美国著名的”精华音乐节“最重要的演出环节，暌违舞台许久的珍妮举办了她2年以来的首场演唱会。并负责拉开了音乐节大幕。<ref name="Gardner">{{citation|last=Gardner|first=Elysa|title=Janet Jackson marries work, personal life in Perry sequel|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2010-04-01-janet01_ST_N.htm|newspaper=USA Today|date=2010-03-31|accessdate=2010-04-07|archive-date=2010-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100404115027/http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2010-04-01-janet01_ST_N.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[美联社|美联社]]报道说："珍妮·杰克逊周五那两个小时的表演使台下的观众如痴如醉，并让所有到场的歌迷都觉得，就算等待了2年也是值得的。”<ref>{{citation|title=Janet Jackson Dazzles Crowd at Essence Festival|work=Billboard|url=http://www.billboard.com/song/janet-jackson/nothing#/news/janet-jackson-dazzles-crowd-at-essence-festival-1004102114.story|date=2010-07-03|accessdate=2010-07-03|archive-date=2011-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605045429/http://www.billboard.com/song/janet-jackson/nothing#/news/janet-jackson-dazzles-crowd-at-essence-festival-1004102114.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年7月，珍妮继[[莲纳·荷恩|莲纳·荷恩]]、[[伊丽莎白·泰勒|伊丽莎白·泰勒]]、[[羅蘭·比歌|劳伦·白考尔]]和[[戴安娜·罗斯|戴安娜·罗斯]]后，成为美国著名毛皮生产协会{{tsl|en|American Legend Cooperative|美国传奇水貂养殖场协会}}的皮草品牌'''宝嘉美'''新一代代言人，并拍摄了名为“怎样才能成为传奇？”的系列广告。<ref name="fur">{{citation|author=Ella Ngo|title=Poll: Are You Fur or Against Janet Jackson's New Ad|url=http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/b192769_poll_are_you_fur_against_janet_jacksons.html#ixzz0v8eHIF1S|publisher=[[E!_Online|E!]]|date=2010-07-29|accessdate=2010-07-29|archive-date=2010-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100801150229/http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/b192769_poll_are_you_fur_against_janet_jacksons.html#ixzz0v8eHIF1S|dead-url=no}}</ref>公司的发言人说，选择珍妮作为代言人是因为她“是世界音乐和娱乐史上的偶像，一个真正的传奇。她向众人充分展示了一代传奇所应该有的所有元素，珍妮在娱乐界的地位也就如同'''宝嘉美'''在奢侈品界的地位一般。”<ref name="fur"/>珍妮的这一广告激怒众多动物权益保障组织以及演艺圈的反皮草人士。<ref name="fur"/>著名影星[[帕米拉·安德森|帕米拉·安德森]]和美国[[善待动物组织|善待动物组织]]的副总裁Dan Mathews均谴责珍妮的这一行为虚伪，因为珍妮也曾经拒绝为皮草广告代言。<ref name="fur2">{{citation|author=Cristina Everett|title=Pamela Anderson slams 'greedy' Janet Jackson for hawking fur in 'disappointing' Blackglama ad|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/2010/07/29/2010-07-29_pamela_anderson_slams_greedy_janet_jackson_for_hawking_fur_in_disappointing_blac.html|publisher=[[Daily_News_(New_York)|Daily News]]|date=2010-07-29|accessdate=2010-07-29|archive-date=2010-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100731055514/http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/2010/07/29/2010-07-29_pamela_anderson_slams_greedy_janet_jackson_for_hawking_fur_in_disappointing_blac.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年8月，环球唱片出版了珍妮第三张精选集《{{tsl|en|Icon: Number Ones|Icon: Number Ones}}》,这是环球唱片《偶像》系列精选集中的一张，这系列精选集的文案中写道：“这系列精选集，是音乐史
最伟大的艺术家们的标志性歌曲以及最广受歌迷喜爱的歌曲集合。”<ref>{{citation|title=Icon Series Launched by Universal Music Enterprises|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/icon-series-launched-by-universal-music-enterprises-100254019.html|publisher=[[PR_Newswire|PR Newswire]]|place=[[Universal_Music_Enterprises|Universal Music Enterprises]]|date=2010-08-09|accessdate=2010-08-09|archive-date=2010-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100817225346/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/icon-series-launched-by-universal-music-enterprises-100254019.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2010年11月，她在Tyler Perry改编自1975年{{tsl|en|Ntozake Shange|Ntozake Shange}}创作的舞台剧《{{tsl|en|For Colored Girls Who Have Considered Suicide When the Rainbow Is Enuf|给那些当彩虹出现，就要考虑自杀的有色女孩}}》(For Colored Girls Who Have Considered Suicide When the Rainbow Is Enuf)的电影《{{tsl|en|For Colored Girls|彩虹艳尽半边天}}》(For Colored Girls)中饰演Joanna。《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》的Christopher John Farley高度赞扬了珍妮在剧中的表演：“当她口中朗读出原作者Ntozake Shange撰写的台词——这整部剧的精髓所在...不仅仅像在咖啡店的轻声细说，更像是一场看似平凡但不可辩驳的演说。”<ref>{{citation|author=Christopher John Farley|title=Janet Jackson Tackles Poetry in ‘For Colored Girls’|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2010/11/02/janet-jackson-tackles-poetry-in-for-colored-girls|newspaper=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]|date=2010-11-02|accessdate=2010-11-02|archive-date=2010-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101105024858/http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2010/11/02/janet-jackson-tackles-poetry-in-for-colored-girls/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而线上杂志[[Salon.com|Salon.com]]的Matt Zoller Seitz则评价她：“她已经远远的超越了自己——尤其是在那场她终于发现自己丈夫的秘密的戏中，珍妮那短发造型，倍受创伤的眼神，导演在珍妮身上激发的戏剧张力，老练世故的表现和孤独冷漠刚毅的女性特质融合在一起，不由的会讓人联想起影坛的一代传奇[[珍·惠曼|珍·惠曼]]和[[琼·克劳馥|琼·克劳馥]]。不得不说，Peryy是一位出色并有巨大洞察力的导演。”<ref name="Seitz">{{citation|author=Matt Zoller Seitz|title='For Colored Girls': Tyler Perry's Misunderstood Genius|url=http://www.salon.com/entertainment/movies/film_salon/2010/11/04/defense_of_tyler_perry/index.html|publisher=[[Salon.com|Salon.com]]|date=2010-11-04|accessdate=2010-11-04|archive-date=2010-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101109045613/http://www.salon.com/entertainment/movies/film_salon/2010/11/04/defense_of_tyler_perry/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>《纽约时报》的Manohla Dargis评论说：“珍妮·杰克逊虽然演出经验不足，但表演的还算得当。但她看似平凡的演出却充满了力量。部分是因为她与她的兄长迈克尔都具有的古怪的个性，契合了剧中角色那乖张、傲慢、自以为是但其实内心极度脆弱的特质，就像{{tsl|en|Lana Turner|Lana Turner}}所塑造的一系列荧幕形象一样，透着一股怪异的真实感。”<ref name="Dargis">{{citation|author=Manohla Dargis|title=A Powerful Chorus Harmonizing ‘Dark Phrases of Womanhood’|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/2010/11/05/movies/05for.html|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2010-11-04|accessdate=2010-11-04|archive-date=2010-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101106081613/http://movies.nytimes.com/2010/11/05/movies/05for.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>部分的影评家还将珍妮的演出与[[梅丽尔·斯特里普|梅莉·史翠普]]在《[[穿普拉达的女王_(电影)|穿著Prada的惡魔]]》中的演出做比较。<ref name="Dargis"/><ref>{{citation|author=Randy Myers|title=Review: Cast elevates 'For Colored Girls' from soap opera territory|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/movies-dvd/ci_16493615|newspaper=[[San_Jose_Mercury_News|San Jose Mercury News]]|date=2010-11-04|accessdate=2010-11-04|archive-date=2012-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206165245/http://www.mercurynews.com/movies-dvd/ci_16493615|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citation|author=Claudia Puig|title=Tyler Perry turns poetic 'For Colored Girls' into a soap opera|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2010-11-05-Forcoloredgirls05_ST_N.htm|newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=2010-11-04|accessdate=2010-11-04|archive-date=2010-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101107001534/http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2010-11-05-Forcoloredgirls05_ST_N.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>她的表现也为她赢得了非裔美国电影人促进基金会举办的2011年{{tsl|en|Black Reel Award|黑盘奖}}最佳女配角奖提名和最佳集体演出奖提名。<ref>{{citation|title=2011 Black Reel Awards Nominations|url=http://blackreelawards.wordpress.com/2010/12/15/2011-black-reel-awards-nominations/|publisher=[[Black_Reel_Awards|Black Reel Awards]]|date=2010-12-15|accessdate=2010-12-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101221000645/http://blackreelawards.wordpress.com/2010/12/15/2011-black-reel-awards-nominations/|archivedate=2010-12-21|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

2010年11月18日，珍妮接受[[美国在线|美国在线]]的音乐节目《The Boombox》的专访，她宣布计划将在2011年举办她个人职业生涯中规模最大的世界巡演。<ref name="2011 tour">{{citation |url=http://www.theboombox.com/2010/11/19/janet-jackson-announces-2011-plans/ |title=Janet Jackson Announces 2011 Plans, Asks Fans for Questions - The Boombox |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |work=The Boombox |date=2010-11-19 |accessdate=2010-11-19 |archive-date=2010-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101121034752/http://www.theboombox.com/2010/11/19/janet-jackson-announces-2011-plans/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="2011 tour">{{citation |url=http://www.theboombox.com/2010/11/19/janet-jackson-announces-2011-plans/ |title=Janet Jackson Announces 2011 Plans, Asks Fans for Questions - The Boombox |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |work=The Boombox |date=2010-11-19 |accessdate=2010-11-19}}</ref>这场名为《{{tsl|en|Number Ones: Up Close and Personal|Number Ones: Up Close and Personal}}》的巡回演唱会将跨越世界上各大洲的35个城市。<ref name="2011 tour"/>而举办的城市地点，将由歌迷在她的官方网站上选出。<ref name="2011 tour"/>而在表演中，她也将自己在各大排行榜上的35首冠军单曲作为礼物奉献给这座城市。<ref name="2011 tour"/>珍妮也与美国玩具公司[[美泰尔|美泰尔]]合作发售以自己为形象的一款限量版的[[芭比娃娃|芭比娃娃]]，命名为“Divinely Janet”。这款娃娃的所有收益也将捐献给美国{{tsl|en|Project Angel Food|天使计划基金会}}。<ref>{{citation|author=Amber Katz|title=This Janet Jackson Barbie Doll Is All We Want For Christmas!|url=http://buzzworthy.mtv.com/2010/12/10/janet-jackson-barbie-doll/|publisher=MTV|date=2010-12-10|accessdate=2011-04-08|archive-date=2010-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101217011008/http://buzzworthy.mtv.com/2010/12/10/janet-jackson-barbie-doll|dead-url=no}}</ref>2011年2月15日，珍妮亲自撰写的首部{{tsl|en|Self-help|自助书}}《{{tsl|en|True You: A Journey to Finding and Loving Yourself|珍我：如何发现自己与爱自己}}》(True You: A Journey to Finding and Loving Yourself)出版发行，并在3月登上了[[纽约时报畅销书榜|纽约时报畅销书榜]]的首位。<ref>{{citation|title=Best Sellers - The New York Times|url=http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2011-03-06/hardcover-advice/list.html|work=The New York Times|date=20011-02-28|accessdate=2011-02-28|archive-date=2011-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110228085646/http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2011-03-06/hardcover-advice/list.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2011年3月，她与[[狮门娱乐|狮门娱乐]]签了一部电影的制作合约，将由自组的独立工作室独立制作与发行一部电影。<ref name="PM">{{citation|author=Pamela McClintock|title=Janet Jackson Signs Film Production Deal with Lionsgate (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/janet-jackson-signs-film-production-167872|newspaper=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2011-03-15|accessdate=2011-03-17|archive-date=2011-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110318085223/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/janet-jackson-signs-film-production-167872|dead-url=no}}</ref>狮门娱乐电影制作与发行部的总裁Mike Paseornek说：“珍妮是一个充满实力的艺人，并深受观众的喜爱。我们深信她会在大荧幕上也给我们带来精彩的演出。我们对能帮助她完成充满激情和才华的构思而深感荣幸。“<ref name="PM"/>随后，珍妮成为第一位在巴黎[[卢浮宫|卢浮宫]]由著名设计师[[贝聿铭|贝聿铭]]设计的玻璃金字塔中表演的女艺人。这场慈善演出也是为了修复卢浮宫的工作而筹集善款。卢浮宫的艺术总监Henri Loyrette说：”作为这个世界最出色的艺术家之一，珍妮·杰克逊让我们深感自豪，她激情四射的演出也和玻璃金字塔同样是这个世界上的杰作之一。“<ref>{{citation|author=Sonya E|title=Janet Jackson To Make History In Paris|url=http://www.s2smagazine.com/stories/2011/04/janet-jackson-make-history-paris|newspaper=[[Sister_2_Sister|Sister 2 Sister]]|date=2011-04-08|accessdate=2011-04-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110411082009/http://www.s2smagazine.com/stories/2011/04/janet-jackson-make-history-paris|archivedate=2011-04-11}}</ref>2011年8月，珍妮宣布与'''宝嘉美'''续约两年，'''宝嘉美'''的CEO Joe Morelli说：”我们在对产品今后的推广工作的讨论中达成共识，觉得珍妮在此前的表现完全符合我们的要求，她的魅力、豪华的特质和精致的品质完全符合'''宝嘉美'''的特点。<ref>{{citation|title=Janet Jackson Featured In New Blackglama Ad Campaign|url=http://www.rttnews.com/Content/EntertainmentNews.aspx?Section=2&Id=1700517&SM=1|publisher=[[RTT_News|RTT News]]|date=2011-08-25|accessdate=2011-08-26|archive-date=2011-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111212163112/http://www.rttnews.com/Content/EntertainmentNews.aspx?Section=2&Id=1700517&SM=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>2011年，珍妮与该品牌合作的15件珍贵的毛皮制品在[[薩克斯第五大道|萨克斯第五大道精品百货店]]和[[布鲁明黛百货公司|布鲁明黛百货公司]]出售。<ref>{{citation|author=Coleen Nika|title=News Roundup: Lady Gaga's Barney's Workshop, Rihanna's Collection, Janet Jackson's New Line And More|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/blogs/thread-count/news-roundup-lady-gagas-barneys-workshop-rihannas-collection-janet-jacksons-new-line-and-more-20111123#ixzz1f5PBzWZB|newspaper=Rolling Stone|date=2011-11-23|accessdate=2011-11-29|archive-date=2011-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111126045215/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/blogs/thread-count/news-roundup-lady-gagas-barneys-workshop-rihannas-collection-janet-jacksons-new-line-and-more-20111123#ixzz1f5PBzWZB|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后她也成为减肥产品制造商{{tsl|en|Nutrisystem|NutriSystem}}代言，并与该公司一起将价值1000万美元的食物捐献给有需要的人群。<ref name="nutri">{{citation|author=Elizabeth Olson|title=Weight Loss, With Divas and Public Service|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/15/business/media/weight-loss-with-divas-and-public-service-angles.html?_r=1|newspaper=New York Times|date=2011-12-14|accessdate=2012-01-03|archive-date=2013-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509125708/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/15/business/media/weight-loss-with-divas-and-public-service-angles.html?_r=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

